WEBVTT

1
00:00:47.583 --> 00:00:49.791
[suspenseful music playing]

2
00:00:52.333 --> 00:00:54.833
[gurgling]

3
00:00:58.458 --> 00:01:00.708
[woman] Hi. my name is Jill.

4
00:01:02.125 --> 00:01:04.458
Hi. my name is Joan.

5
00:01:05.583 --> 00:01:06.416
My name…

6
00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:09.375
DESIRE

7
00:01:09.458 --> 00:01:11.625
[suspenseful music continues]

8
00:01:15.625 --> 00:01:18.291
[gasps and screams]

9
00:01:18.375 --> 00:01:20.375
LOMAS CLUB

10
00:01:23.583 --> 00:01:29.583
ONE MONTH EARLIER

11
00:01:32.416 --> 00:01:34.625
[intriguing music playing]

12
00:02:00.875 --> 00:02:02.208
[man] Good morning.

13
00:02:03.958 --> 00:02:05.375
[music fades]

14
00:02:45.541 --> 00:02:47.625
-These. right?
-Mom. which perfume should I wear?

15
00:02:47.708 --> 00:02:50.125
-Can I use one of yours?
-Whatever you want. Yes. my dear.

16
00:02:50.208 --> 00:02:51.583
But only a little.

17
00:02:51.666 --> 00:02:53.166
The other dress looked better.

18
00:02:53.250 --> 00:02:55.958
Yes. thank you. my love.
And the white button up?

19
00:02:56.041 --> 00:02:58.000
Uh… I changed.
I wanted something different.

20
00:02:58.083 --> 00:02:59.583
-Does it look bad?
-You look handsome.

21
00:02:59.666 --> 00:03:02.083
-Yeah? You sure?
-Come on. Let's go. honey. come on.

22
00:03:03.041 --> 00:03:04.958
[sighs] I think we invited
too many people.

23
00:03:05.041 --> 00:03:07.666
-You'll be fine. It'll be a great time.
-Mm.

24
00:03:08.458 --> 00:03:11.791
-Look at you.
-Oh. my boy. you look so good.

25
00:03:12.541 --> 00:03:15.041
So put together and handsome.

26
00:03:15.125 --> 00:03:17.791
[young man] Wow! I can't believe
we're actually related. [chuckles]

27
00:03:17.875 --> 00:03:19.166
Don't say that!

28
00:03:19.250 --> 00:03:20.958
We look exactly alike.

29
00:03:21.041 --> 00:03:22.041
Hey.

30
00:03:23.375 --> 00:03:25.916
Thank you. It means a lot to me.

31
00:03:26.625 --> 00:03:28.458
-We're a team.
-[young woman] A team.

32
00:03:28.541 --> 00:03:29.375
[all] A team.

33
00:03:29.458 --> 00:03:31.291
[party guests chatter indistinctly]

34
00:03:31.375 --> 00:03:33.958
[partygoers welcome them]

35
00:03:35.916 --> 00:03:37.916
[classical music playing]

36
00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:40.583
Thanks. Thank you!

37
00:03:41.208 --> 00:03:44.083
-How are you not totally embarrassed?
-I am embarrassed.

38
00:03:45.333 --> 00:03:47.250
[clapping]

39
00:03:47.333 --> 00:03:49.500
Thanks. guys! Thanks!

40
00:03:51.458 --> 00:03:52.500
[classical music ends]

41
00:03:52.583 --> 00:03:55.125
It's so good to see all your lovely faces.

42
00:03:55.208 --> 00:03:56.833
Thank you for being here.

43
00:03:56.916 --> 00:03:59.666
Today we celebrate 20 years of marriage.

44
00:03:59.750 --> 00:04:05.125
And in these years. we've created
memories that are irreplaceable.

45
00:04:05.625 --> 00:04:08.541
And more importantly.
our beautiful children.

46
00:04:08.625 --> 00:04:10.958
But we've had hard moments too.

47
00:04:11.041 --> 00:04:12.458
As any couple does.

48
00:04:13.291 --> 00:04:16.875
Because love… isn't perfect.

49
00:04:17.791 --> 00:04:19.375
Or meant to be easy.

50
00:04:19.875 --> 00:04:23.458
But true love is when you.
uh. decide to stay.

51
00:04:23.541 --> 00:04:26.458
and choose each other again and again.

52
00:04:27.416 --> 00:04:30.000
-Thank you. my love. for our journey.
-[chuckles]

53
00:04:30.083 --> 00:04:31.916
And for always fighting for us.

54
00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:34.333
So once again. I choose you.

55
00:04:35.291 --> 00:04:39.000
to create more memories
for the rest of our days. Thank you.

56
00:04:39.083 --> 00:04:41.541
[cheering and applause]

57
00:04:41.625 --> 00:04:43.583
-[man] Bravo!
-[woman] Long live love!

58
00:04:43.666 --> 00:04:44.916
Woo!

59
00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.166
-I love you.
-I love you.

60
00:04:46.250 --> 00:04:48.375
[all] Cheers!

61
00:04:49.791 --> 00:04:51.208
[classical music ends]

62
00:04:53.458 --> 00:04:54.625
Where's your mom?

63
00:04:54.708 --> 00:04:56.708
-Over there.
-Ah.

64
00:04:56.791 --> 00:04:59.666
-[man] Lucero. my dearest friend.
-Maybe I'll go next time.

65
00:04:59.750 --> 00:05:02.041
Congratulations!

66
00:05:02.125 --> 00:05:03.166
You look amazing.

67
00:05:03.833 --> 00:05:07.875
You two are the only hope
for true love in this world.

68
00:05:07.958 --> 00:05:09.791
No. seriously. you look radiant.

69
00:05:09.875 --> 00:05:13.833
-Oh man. you look terrible. What happened?
-[chuckles]

70
00:05:13.916 --> 00:05:15.708
-Yeah. right.
-[pouring drink]

71
00:05:15.791 --> 00:05:17.583
Hard times we are living through. right?

72
00:05:17.666 --> 00:05:18.916
-Yeah. sure.
-Mm.

73
00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:21.375
Could we do this another time?
Just please. not here.

74
00:05:21.458 --> 00:05:24.375
Lucero. I'm the District Attorney
of Mexico City.

75
00:05:24.458 --> 00:05:25.708
-I need you to help me.
-I will.

76
00:05:25.791 --> 00:05:27.583
-Okay.
-But… but not right now.

77
00:05:27.666 --> 00:05:29.375
We'll talk tomorrow at your house.

78
00:05:29.458 --> 00:05:31.791
Yeah. right. My house?

79
00:05:31.875 --> 00:05:33.875
Malena kicked me out of the house.

80
00:05:33.958 --> 00:05:36.833
Get it? I'm living in a damn hotel.
I haven't slept in three days.

81
00:05:36.916 --> 00:05:39.276
-I need you to help me.
-Yes. I'll help you. I already said.

82
00:05:39.333 --> 00:05:41.375
-Hey. congratulations. Fernando.
-Thanks. what's up?

83
00:05:41.458 --> 00:05:43.041
-How are you?
-Good. good.

84
00:05:43.125 --> 00:05:44.666
[slow jazz music playing]

85
00:05:44.750 --> 00:05:47.958
[Fernando] Give me a champagne
and a whiskey. please.

86
00:05:48.041 --> 00:05:50.250
[sighs softly]

87
00:05:50.333 --> 00:05:51.708
-So what is it?
-Mm?

88
00:05:52.625 --> 00:05:53.750
Alma.

89
00:05:54.250 --> 00:05:56.833
What's the secret to everlasting love?

90
00:05:59.791 --> 00:06:01.000
No secret.

91
00:06:02.125 --> 00:06:03.416
Just patience.

92
00:06:06.125 --> 00:06:12.041
Understanding that… there are things
you don't argue about more than once.

93
00:06:12.875 --> 00:06:14.166
Um…

94
00:06:14.250 --> 00:06:16.500
And always being there when she needs me.

95
00:06:17.041 --> 00:06:20.291
Helping her through anything
that life may throw at her.

96
00:06:21.083 --> 00:06:23.666
Doing everything I can
to make her dreams come true.

97
00:06:23.750 --> 00:06:26.375
No matter what that could mean for me.

98
00:06:26.458 --> 00:06:29.708
[Alma sighs] Where can I find
a man like you?

99
00:06:38.666 --> 00:06:40.375
[Fernando] I had a wonderful time.

100
00:06:41.416 --> 00:06:42.875
I'm so glad.

101
00:06:49.666 --> 00:06:51.125
[Fernando kisses]

102
00:06:52.458 --> 00:06:55.791
[uneasy music playing]

103
00:06:56.375 --> 00:06:58.875
[Lucero] This is getting
harder and harder for me.

104
00:07:00.458 --> 00:07:03.083
[Fernando] What do you mean?
You're a natural.

105
00:07:03.708 --> 00:07:05.541
I'm only pretending.

106
00:07:07.500 --> 00:07:09.958
[Fernando] Well. you're very good at it.

107
00:07:12.583 --> 00:07:14.583
[Lucero] I've had a great teacher.

108
00:07:18.583 --> 00:07:21.166
Alma looked so beautiful. didn't she?

109
00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:23.791
[Fernando] So beautiful.

110
00:07:23.875 --> 00:07:26.000
[Lucero] She's been acting
very mysterious lately.

111
00:07:28.666 --> 00:07:31.208
It's almost like she has a secret.

112
00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:36.500
See couldn't keep her eyes off you
all afternoon.

113
00:07:36.583 --> 00:07:37.416
[Fernando sighs]

114
00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:39.125
She's into you.

115
00:07:39.208 --> 00:07:41.583
[chuckles] She's just like that.

116
00:07:44.166 --> 00:07:46.916
[Lucero] Oh yeah? Do you like Alma?

117
00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:49.166
[uneasy music continues]

118
00:07:49.250 --> 00:07:51.166
You don't have to lie.

119
00:07:52.875 --> 00:07:54.416
I like you.

120
00:07:58.333 --> 00:07:59.583
Yes. but…

121
00:08:00.583 --> 00:08:02.125
Do you like her?

122
00:08:09.833 --> 00:08:11.708
Should we invite her over?

123
00:08:17.083 --> 00:08:19.250
Don't tell me
you've never thought about it.

124
00:08:21.583 --> 00:08:24.166
I think it's you
who's been thinking about it.

125
00:08:28.666 --> 00:08:29.791
Am I wrong?

126
00:08:32.541 --> 00:08:33.541
Huh?

127
00:08:37.958 --> 00:08:40.166
[uneasy music continues]

128
00:08:46.791 --> 00:08:48.708
What I really want is you.

129
00:08:50.041 --> 00:08:52.666
But. I just…
How long has it been since you and I…?

130
00:08:52.750 --> 00:08:54.166
You don't think I know?

131
00:08:55.458 --> 00:08:58.250
But do you really want
to talk about that right now?

132
00:08:59.041 --> 00:09:01.000
Well. then tell me when.

133
00:09:01.083 --> 00:09:03.333
Am I supposed to schedule
an appointment with you?

134
00:09:03.416 --> 00:09:04.416
Okay. perfect.

135
00:09:05.583 --> 00:09:06.833
Let's talk.

136
00:09:08.500 --> 00:09:12.000
Are you…?
Are you proposing seeing someone else?

137
00:09:16.166 --> 00:09:18.625
Seriously. is that what you want?

138
00:09:21.333 --> 00:09:22.583
[Lucero sighs]

139
00:09:25.125 --> 00:09:27.291
You're right. We've had a big day.

140
00:09:27.375 --> 00:09:29.750
[music turns gentle]

141
00:09:34.583 --> 00:09:36.208
We'll talk tomorrow.

142
00:09:40.750 --> 00:09:42.041
[music fades]

143
00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:52.625
Mom. don't forget that I have
the timed trials tomorrow.

144
00:09:52.708 --> 00:09:53.541
-Okay?
-Okay.

145
00:09:53.625 --> 00:09:55.083
No. thank you. Give me a second.

146
00:09:55.166 --> 00:09:56.333
-Uh. babe?
-[Lucero] Mm?

147
00:09:56.416 --> 00:10:00.041
Could you refill my drops. please?
I won't have time to go to the pharmacy.

148
00:10:00.125 --> 00:10:01.805
-Sorry. Javi.
-I added a little more water.

149
00:10:01.875 --> 00:10:04.226
I won't have time to drink it.
Can you put it in the fridge?

150
00:10:04.250 --> 00:10:06.290
-Javi. I don't want to get into it...
-I have to go.

151
00:10:06.333 --> 00:10:08.333
No. no. they're not.

152
00:10:08.416 --> 00:10:09.250
-Leaving?
-Yeah.

153
00:10:09.333 --> 00:10:10.750
-We were gonna talk about…
-We will.

154
00:10:10.833 --> 00:10:13.125
I'm going to the club.
I have suppliers waiting. Sorry.

155
00:10:13.208 --> 00:10:15.583
Kids. I'm leaving too.
See you later. okay?

156
00:10:15.666 --> 00:10:18.375
-Mom. hey. pick me up from swimming today.
-Yup.

157
00:10:18.458 --> 00:10:19.458
[Viviana] Bye.

158
00:10:20.458 --> 00:10:22.958
[tense music playing]

159
00:10:31.208 --> 00:10:33.208
[music fades]

160
00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:36.000
[traffic noise]

161
00:10:37.041 --> 00:10:40.708
[D.A.] I'll be waiting at the hotel bar.
The entrance is a bit hidden.

162
00:10:40.791 --> 00:10:43.041
It's a very private place.
Ask at reception.

163
00:10:43.125 --> 00:10:44.250
See you there.

164
00:10:49.791 --> 00:10:52.642
-[receptionist] …it's the exact same size.
-[man] Including my five dogs?

165
00:10:52.666 --> 00:10:56.166
[receptionist] Five Dogs? That wasn't
in the… in the reservation. Hold on.

166
00:10:56.666 --> 00:10:58.750
-[Lucero] Excuse me. ma'am.
-I understand.

167
00:10:58.833 --> 00:10:59.875
[Lucero] Ma'am?

168
00:11:00.541 --> 00:11:03.500
-Excuse me. Where is the bar?
-Sorry. I'll be with you in a moment.

169
00:11:03.583 --> 00:11:07.625
My kids are crying right now
because this hotel doesn't accept pets…

170
00:11:10.625 --> 00:11:13.541
-[Lucero] Excuse me. where is the bar?
-[man] Straight down the hall.

171
00:11:22.500 --> 00:11:24.375
[Lucero] Oh! Hi.

172
00:11:25.041 --> 00:11:27.875
Sorry. I got lost.
I'm trying to find the bar.

173
00:11:27.958 --> 00:11:31.166
Ah. yes. Go all the way down the hall
and it's on the left.

174
00:11:31.250 --> 00:11:32.958
[Lucero] Ah! Great. Thank you.

175
00:12:01.625 --> 00:12:04.583
["Quiero Amanecer Con Alguien"
by Daniela Romo playing in bar]

176
00:12:13.375 --> 00:12:15.791
[indistinct chatter]

177
00:12:24.666 --> 00:12:25.666
[sighs]

178
00:12:28.291 --> 00:12:29.458
[Lucero] Hey.

179
00:12:30.500 --> 00:12:31.666
Sorry.

180
00:12:32.666 --> 00:12:35.125
[Lucero] What a weird place.
This was so hard to find.

181
00:12:35.208 --> 00:12:36.500
Oh.

182
00:12:36.583 --> 00:12:37.625
-Yeah.
-How are you?

183
00:12:38.250 --> 00:12:41.666
-You don't look much better.
-No? You don't say.

184
00:12:41.750 --> 00:12:44.000
-Two more. please.
-One.

185
00:12:44.083 --> 00:12:45.833
-Oh. come on.
-No.

186
00:12:46.583 --> 00:12:47.916
Is this where you brought her?

187
00:12:49.708 --> 00:12:50.708
[Lucero chuckles]

188
00:12:51.291 --> 00:12:54.916
-God. I can't believe you. you asshole.
-Oh. yeah?

189
00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:56.833
And you've been married
how many years now?

190
00:12:56.916 --> 00:12:58.708
-Twenty.
-Twenty.

191
00:12:58.791 --> 00:13:02.666
And you're going to tell me
that you've had good sex for 20 years? Hm?

192
00:13:02.750 --> 00:13:03.750
-Yes.
-Yes?

193
00:13:03.833 --> 00:13:04.666
Mm-hmm.

194
00:13:04.750 --> 00:13:06.208
Come on. Lucero.

195
00:13:06.833 --> 00:13:07.958
There's gotta be more.

196
00:13:08.041 --> 00:13:11.583
You can't possibly spend your whole life
going from home to work. work to home.

197
00:13:11.666 --> 00:13:13.125
and Sundays with the in-laws.

198
00:13:13.208 --> 00:13:17.958
You gotta live here in the moment.
Romance. passion. and sex.

199
00:13:18.041 --> 00:13:20.041
-[chuckles]
-All things a man needs.

200
00:13:20.125 --> 00:13:22.525
Oh. no. Please don't give me that.
because women need it too.

201
00:13:22.583 --> 00:13:24.083
Exactly! Men and women…

202
00:13:24.166 --> 00:13:25.000
[phone buzzing]

203
00:13:25.083 --> 00:13:27.333
…want their needs met.
I just happened to get caught.

204
00:13:27.416 --> 00:13:29.416
It was a miscalculation.

205
00:13:29.500 --> 00:13:31.000
Miscalculation?

206
00:13:33.458 --> 00:13:34.375
-What's with you?
-Hmm?

207
00:13:34.458 --> 00:13:35.958
Who are you looking at?

208
00:13:36.500 --> 00:13:38.125
No one. it's just…

209
00:13:39.250 --> 00:13:41.833
I'm just constantly scared
of them following me now.

210
00:13:41.916 --> 00:13:43.375
Just take a deep breath.

211
00:13:43.458 --> 00:13:45.625
It's okay. It's alright.

212
00:13:45.708 --> 00:13:47.333
It's going to be fine.

213
00:13:48.166 --> 00:13:49.250
[sighs]

214
00:13:49.333 --> 00:13:51.833
Oh. Lucero.
they're going to take the girls.

215
00:13:51.916 --> 00:13:55.708
I'm going to help you. Really.
We'll get through this.

216
00:13:56.333 --> 00:13:58.000
You're not going to lose your daughters.

217
00:13:58.708 --> 00:14:01.017
She won't take their father away.
She just wants the house.

218
00:14:01.041 --> 00:14:04.458
Okay sure. and? She's a bitch.
she's angry and for a good reason.

219
00:14:04.541 --> 00:14:07.291
Look. Trust me. huh?

220
00:14:07.375 --> 00:14:08.958
I trust you.

221
00:14:09.708 --> 00:14:11.833
[cell phone buzzes]

222
00:14:11.916 --> 00:14:13.416
Excuse me. please.

223
00:14:26.875 --> 00:14:29.958
Sorry. darling. I have to go.
Something came up I have to deal with.

224
00:14:30.041 --> 00:14:32.250
Sure. no problem. I should be going too.

225
00:14:32.333 --> 00:14:35.083
You look terrible.
Shave. do something. Shower.

226
00:14:35.166 --> 00:14:37.000
Thank you. Thanks. yeah. Bye.

227
00:14:55.833 --> 00:14:59.250
["Quiero Amanecer Con Alguien"
continues playing]

228
00:15:38.916 --> 00:15:42.208
-Yeah?
-We set up the security cameras yesterday.

229
00:15:42.291 --> 00:15:44.833
-Should I install the app for monitoring?
-Yes. would you?

230
00:15:45.708 --> 00:15:47.291
Thanks. Lau.

231
00:15:47.375 --> 00:15:49.875
[man] I replaced it. and now
the photometer is showing.

232
00:15:49.958 --> 00:15:54.416
Hold on. Cami. the pots for the plants.
please. out of the hallway.

233
00:15:54.500 --> 00:15:56.166
Chlorine and pH equilibrium.

234
00:15:56.250 --> 00:15:59.125
And the valve has pressure
to pull in the propane.

235
00:15:59.208 --> 00:16:00.416
-You fixed it?
-It's ready.

236
00:16:00.500 --> 00:16:03.666
Really? That's great.
This thing is 30 years old.

237
00:16:03.750 --> 00:16:05.041
It's done.

238
00:16:05.625 --> 00:16:06.458
So it's all set?

239
00:16:06.541 --> 00:16:08.541
[inaudible]

240
00:16:17.125 --> 00:16:18.208
That's it.

241
00:16:20.625 --> 00:16:21.916
[chuckles]

242
00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:23.083
Come here.

243
00:16:25.458 --> 00:16:27.416
Please. Keep your…

244
00:16:27.500 --> 00:16:29.791
Stay back a little
to give them room. okay?

245
00:16:29.875 --> 00:16:31.583
It's the older girls' turn now.

246
00:16:35.166 --> 00:16:36.083
[clapping]

247
00:16:36.166 --> 00:16:37.750
You're just in time.

248
00:16:38.375 --> 00:16:40.625
Hmm. Did I miss anything?

249
00:16:40.708 --> 00:16:43.541
-No.
-No. no. no. but the new coach is here.

250
00:16:43.625 --> 00:16:45.750
Great find. Fernando.
He is just wonderful.

251
00:16:45.833 --> 00:16:49.583
Hello. everyone. My name is Matías.
I'm your daughters' new coach.

252
00:16:49.666 --> 00:16:50.541
Uh…

253
00:16:50.625 --> 00:16:53.625
Well. obviously.
that's why I'm up here. I. uh…

254
00:16:53.708 --> 00:16:56.750
I was selected to be
in the Olympics in Spain and…

255
00:16:56.833 --> 00:17:00.083
And I really want to give this job my all
so they maybe can do something. well.

256
00:17:00.166 --> 00:17:01.583
do something similar.

257
00:17:01.666 --> 00:17:04.958
And. uh. I hope to… create champions.

258
00:17:05.041 --> 00:17:07.166
And you. girls. forget about your parents.

259
00:17:07.250 --> 00:17:08.791
Today is the first training session.

260
00:17:08.875 --> 00:17:11.500
but I want you to give it your all
right from the start. okay?

261
00:17:11.583 --> 00:17:13.708
-A session where you don't…
-You okay?

262
00:17:14.291 --> 00:17:15.333
Yeah.

263
00:17:15.833 --> 00:17:17.875
I ran into him this morning.

264
00:17:17.958 --> 00:17:20.833
[Matías] If you come here.
it's to give absolutely everything.

265
00:17:20.916 --> 00:17:22.625
-Everything.
-And?

266
00:17:22.708 --> 00:17:24.958
Yeah… that was it.

267
00:17:25.041 --> 00:17:26.833
Absolute commitment.

268
00:17:26.916 --> 00:17:28.833
Listen to me and I'll make you champions.

269
00:17:28.916 --> 00:17:30.083
Take your positions.

270
00:17:30.166 --> 00:17:31.500
Ready?

271
00:17:32.583 --> 00:17:33.791
Go.

272
00:17:33.875 --> 00:17:37.250
[cheering and clapping]

273
00:17:41.666 --> 00:17:44.458
[Matías] Bring your goggles tomorrow.
The other ones.

274
00:17:44.541 --> 00:17:45.541
Matías.

275
00:17:47.416 --> 00:17:49.041
-[Matías] How are you?
-[Fernando] Good.

276
00:17:49.125 --> 00:17:52.000
Hey. great speech.
and a great session. huh? Congratulations.

277
00:17:52.083 --> 00:17:55.291
It was nothing. I am very appreciative.
Thank you for the opportunity.

278
00:17:55.375 --> 00:17:57.791
But results are
what we'll be hoping to see.

279
00:17:58.541 --> 00:18:00.958
Nice to meet you.
I'm Lucero. Viviana's mother.

280
00:18:01.041 --> 00:18:03.833
-It's so nice to finally…
-I'm ready to go. See you tomorrow?

281
00:18:03.916 --> 00:18:05.791
Yes. Amazing work today.

282
00:18:05.875 --> 00:18:08.250
You're a natural. [chuckles]

283
00:18:08.333 --> 00:18:10.500
-So sweet. Come on now.
-Okay. Let's go.

284
00:18:10.583 --> 00:18:11.625
-You ready?
-Yeah. yeah.

285
00:18:11.708 --> 00:18:13.708
-Whatever you need. just ask.
-Thank you.

286
00:18:13.791 --> 00:18:17.708
Can I have more time with the coach?
It's the only way I'll improve.

287
00:18:17.791 --> 00:18:20.375
Oh. same here.
Whatever you need. I'm here.

288
00:18:20.458 --> 00:18:21.666
Anything.

289
00:18:24.958 --> 00:18:27.583
[water running]

290
00:18:31.416 --> 00:18:34.166
[contemplative music playing]

291
00:18:54.833 --> 00:18:56.125
[Lucero moans softly]

292
00:18:56.875 --> 00:18:58.875
[moans]

293
00:19:05.291 --> 00:19:06.791
[moans]

294
00:19:18.708 --> 00:19:22.541
[breathing heavily]

295
00:19:30.083 --> 00:19:31.541
[breathes faster]

296
00:19:31.625 --> 00:19:34.083
[music continues]

297
00:19:57.333 --> 00:20:00.333
[uneasy music playing]

298
00:20:05.958 --> 00:20:07.958
[water continues running]

299
00:20:22.625 --> 00:20:24.041
[sighs]

300
00:20:26.125 --> 00:20:28.083
-[Lucero] Good morning.
-[Ávila] Good morning.

301
00:20:28.166 --> 00:20:30.708
How are you. sir? Hello. Malena.

302
00:20:31.583 --> 00:20:35.625
-Is Mr. Peña not joining us?
-Unfortunately. he won't be able to.

303
00:20:35.708 --> 00:20:38.833
He really tried to be here.
but he's stuck at the courthouse.

304
00:20:39.583 --> 00:20:40.833
This is our proposal.

305
00:20:43.041 --> 00:20:45.125
NOTICE OF DOCUMENT SUBMISSION
TO THE COURT

306
00:20:45.208 --> 00:20:48.083
My client is willing
to reach a fair resolution.

307
00:20:48.666 --> 00:20:50.000
This isn't what Miguel offered.

308
00:20:50.083 --> 00:20:51.708
However. he is not going to buy

309
00:20:51.791 --> 00:20:55.000
into this narrative of victim hood
being constructed here.

310
00:20:55.833 --> 00:20:59.541
This has been presented as a moral case.
when in fact it is a legal matter. sir.

311
00:20:59.625 --> 00:21:01.875
[Ávila] It doesn't appear
to be in good faith.

312
00:21:01.958 --> 00:21:04.166
I'm going to have to review it
and get back to you.

313
00:21:04.250 --> 00:21:07.833
This is more than a narrative. Counselor.
This is a betrayal.

314
00:21:07.916 --> 00:21:11.083
Well. I'm not positive
a judge would agree.

315
00:21:19.750 --> 00:21:21.458
[Lucero exhales]

316
00:21:21.541 --> 00:21:22.541
I'm sorry.

317
00:21:23.041 --> 00:21:24.416
Tell me why you're doing this.

318
00:21:24.500 --> 00:21:27.041
It's not personal. Malena.
I'm doing my job.

319
00:21:27.125 --> 00:21:29.833
You know perfectly well
the things he has done to me.

320
00:21:31.291 --> 00:21:32.833
Help me. I'm begging you.

321
00:21:32.916 --> 00:21:34.708
I can't. Malena.

322
00:21:36.125 --> 00:21:39.541
In fact. I shouldn't even be having
this conversation with you.

323
00:21:41.166 --> 00:21:43.375
Lucero. this isn't a case.

324
00:21:43.458 --> 00:21:46.125
-This is my life. My children's lives.
-[elevator bell rings]

325
00:21:47.750 --> 00:21:49.500
[Lucero] I have to go.

326
00:21:49.583 --> 00:21:51.125
[elevator doors open]

327
00:21:54.458 --> 00:21:55.625
[door close]

328
00:21:55.708 --> 00:21:58.750
["Como Un Títere"
by Amanda Miguel playing]

329
00:21:59.833 --> 00:22:01.041
[sighs]

330
00:22:07.375 --> 00:22:08.541
[cell phone buzzes]

331
00:22:09.750 --> 00:22:12.851
[Miguel] Lucero. sorry. I won't be able
to make it. I'm still at the courthouse.

332
00:22:12.875 --> 00:22:14.625
I'll call you when I leave. okay?

333
00:22:31.083 --> 00:22:32.583
[footsteps approach]

334
00:22:40.125 --> 00:22:42.791
[easy-listening music playing on elevator]

335
00:22:58.666 --> 00:23:00.875
[tense music playing]

336
00:23:19.541 --> 00:23:21.500
[music fades]

337
00:23:22.125 --> 00:23:23.666
[man] Matías. I'm leaving!

338
00:23:23.750 --> 00:23:26.416
[Matías] Okay. sounds good.
Don't worry about closing up. I got it.

339
00:23:27.416 --> 00:23:29.625
-[Octavio] See you tomorrow!
-[Matías] See you tomorrow.

340
00:23:29.708 --> 00:23:31.041
[door closes]

341
00:23:40.958 --> 00:23:43.666
[contemplative music playing]

342
00:23:43.750 --> 00:23:45.166
[exhales]

343
00:24:08.541 --> 00:24:10.541
[splash]

344
00:24:12.375 --> 00:24:14.375
[music continues]

345
00:25:16.916 --> 00:25:18.625
[music fades]

346
00:25:18.708 --> 00:25:21.375
[panting]

347
00:25:21.458 --> 00:25:23.458
[panting]

348
00:25:30.041 --> 00:25:31.416
[both panting]

349
00:25:33.041 --> 00:25:34.375
[Lucero chuckles]

350
00:25:35.000 --> 00:25:37.000
[thunder rolls]

351
00:25:39.041 --> 00:25:41.041
[car approaching]

352
00:25:45.708 --> 00:25:49.291
[Lucero] Hey! Matías. it's going to rain.

353
00:25:49.375 --> 00:25:50.708
Do you want a ride?

354
00:25:54.958 --> 00:25:56.958
[opera music playing in car]

355
00:26:03.791 --> 00:26:08.041
So. why is a champion training girls
on the other side of the world?

356
00:26:11.625 --> 00:26:13.875
Well. I'm injured so I can't compete.

357
00:26:14.958 --> 00:26:17.625
Oh. that's awful. I'm really sorry.

358
00:26:17.708 --> 00:26:20.875
I mean. obviously.
it was hard at the time. but now I…

359
00:26:21.500 --> 00:26:23.166
Now I'm free of the pressure.

360
00:26:23.250 --> 00:26:27.416
So I can. well. I can pursue other things.

361
00:26:30.833 --> 00:26:32.208
I think you'll do amazing things.

362
00:26:33.958 --> 00:26:36.125
You have that sparkle in your eyes.

363
00:26:39.750 --> 00:26:42.458
I'm flattered. [chuckles]

364
00:26:44.416 --> 00:26:46.125
No! It was that way. That way.

365
00:26:46.208 --> 00:26:49.166
-[laughing] You have to tell me earlier.
-On the right. Back that way.

366
00:26:49.250 --> 00:26:53.333
-I haven't driven through here in years.
-Just turn around. There. and turn left.

367
00:26:54.291 --> 00:26:55.833
You know the area?

368
00:26:55.916 --> 00:26:58.416
Yes. Yes. I knew it very well.

369
00:26:58.500 --> 00:27:01.208
Actually. I used to live
a few blocks away.

370
00:27:01.291 --> 00:27:03.125
-No shit!
-Mm-hmm.

371
00:27:04.708 --> 00:27:05.750
Right around here?

372
00:27:05.833 --> 00:27:07.125
[chuckles]

373
00:27:08.333 --> 00:27:09.833
I never would have guessed that.

374
00:27:09.916 --> 00:27:11.250
[chuckling]

375
00:27:11.333 --> 00:27:13.291
I have many secrets.

376
00:27:16.083 --> 00:27:18.875
[opera music continues]

377
00:27:19.833 --> 00:27:21.250
[Matías chuckles]

378
00:27:22.541 --> 00:27:26.333
-Okay.
-This is it. Thank you for the ride.

379
00:27:32.041 --> 00:27:33.166
Good night.

380
00:27:43.875 --> 00:27:45.625
[chuckles] I'm sorry.

381
00:27:49.666 --> 00:27:51.291
When will I see you again?

382
00:27:52.083 --> 00:27:53.625
At the competition.

383
00:27:55.083 --> 00:27:57.166
[chuckling] At the competition?

384
00:27:57.250 --> 00:27:59.791
-It's in a month.
-You better get training. then.

385
00:27:59.875 --> 00:28:02.166
Maybe next time
you'll beat me if you're lucky.

386
00:28:12.708 --> 00:28:13.708
Thanks again.

387
00:28:21.375 --> 00:28:23.416
[laughing]

388
00:28:29.958 --> 00:28:31.416
[exhales]

389
00:28:36.541 --> 00:28:37.916
[music stops]

390
00:28:47.250 --> 00:28:49.333
[thunder rolls]

391
00:28:58.208 --> 00:28:59.541
[door closes]

392
00:29:15.291 --> 00:29:16.541
[sniffs]

393
00:29:18.583 --> 00:29:20.583
[tense music playing]

394
00:29:22.458 --> 00:29:24.458
[exhales]

395
00:29:47.958 --> 00:29:49.958
[sighs]

396
00:29:50.875 --> 00:29:53.166
[music continues]

397
00:29:54.250 --> 00:29:55.416
[sighs]

398
00:30:04.000 --> 00:30:06.000
[breathing heavily]

399
00:30:07.625 --> 00:30:09.791
[footsteps approach]

400
00:30:09.875 --> 00:30:11.083
[door opens]

401
00:30:12.375 --> 00:30:13.791
[Fernando] Busy night?

402
00:30:14.708 --> 00:30:18.458
Yeah. I didn't have time
to go to the pool this morning.

403
00:30:19.666 --> 00:30:21.666
[thunder rolls]

404
00:30:29.583 --> 00:30:31.166
[Fernando] How did it go with Malena?

405
00:30:32.500 --> 00:30:34.125
[Lucero] It was difficult.

406
00:30:34.208 --> 00:30:35.250
Very difficult.

407
00:30:35.750 --> 00:30:36.958
[Fernando] I'm sorry.

408
00:30:38.791 --> 00:30:40.666
Come to bed. I want to hear all about it.

409
00:30:45.625 --> 00:30:49.625
Oh. I'm cramping so bad.
I don't want to go swimming today.

410
00:30:49.708 --> 00:30:51.750
You're in the home stretch. baby.

411
00:30:51.833 --> 00:30:53.375
-Not feeling well?
-Mm-mm.

412
00:30:53.458 --> 00:30:56.083
Ah. that's a shame.
because yesterday I was with Matías.

413
00:30:56.166 --> 00:30:58.208
and he told me to call him
for more lessons.

414
00:30:58.291 --> 00:31:00.333
Wait. seriously? Oh. thank you!

415
00:31:00.958 --> 00:31:03.666
-You're the best.
-God. you're totally obsessed.

416
00:31:03.750 --> 00:31:04.750
Julián.

417
00:31:05.250 --> 00:31:07.708
Well. at least I'm good at something.
unlike you.

418
00:31:08.375 --> 00:31:10.125
-Oh. yeah?
-Mm-hmm.

419
00:31:10.208 --> 00:31:13.041
Maybe I'm just not
totally desperate to impress a guy.

420
00:31:13.125 --> 00:31:14.958
-[Viviana] Hmm.
-[text message dings]

421
00:31:15.041 --> 00:31:17.250
M: HI BOSS…

422
00:31:17.333 --> 00:31:20.791
M: IT'S THE LOSER FROM LAST NIGHT

423
00:31:20.875 --> 00:31:22.416
[cheering]

424
00:31:31.375 --> 00:31:34.208
[cheering continues]

425
00:31:35.541 --> 00:31:36.875
[Matías] New record!

426
00:31:36.958 --> 00:31:39.833
[cheering]

427
00:31:39.916 --> 00:31:41.750
One. zero nine.

428
00:31:41.833 --> 00:31:43.750
-Yes!
-[Matías] Very good. Amazing job.

429
00:31:43.833 --> 00:31:46.958
I really like that stroke.
it's very powerful. You see that. Lucía?

430
00:31:47.041 --> 00:31:50.208
The way she places her chin right up
against her arm like that. Bam!

431
00:31:50.291 --> 00:31:53.750
It's unbelievable. It was almost poetry.
It was art. Incredible.

432
00:31:53.833 --> 00:31:55.666
-[Lucero] Hey.
-Incredible.

433
00:31:55.750 --> 00:31:57.000
Look.

434
00:31:57.083 --> 00:31:58.750
Mom. what are you doing here?

435
00:31:58.833 --> 00:32:01.000
-I've come to pick you up like you asked.
-No.

436
00:32:01.083 --> 00:32:05.208
-I told you I'm getting a ride with Lucía.
-Oh. I'm sorry. sweetie.

437
00:32:05.291 --> 00:32:06.750
Well. how did it go?

438
00:32:06.833 --> 00:32:09.541
-Vi beat her time by a full second.
-[gasps]

439
00:32:09.625 --> 00:32:11.375
That's amazing!

440
00:32:11.458 --> 00:32:13.416
-My princess.
-Thank you.

441
00:32:13.875 --> 00:32:16.958
Matías. did you know that. uh.
Lucero. when she was our age.

442
00:32:17.041 --> 00:32:18.375
she was already in the nationals.

443
00:32:18.458 --> 00:32:21.333
-[Matías] No way.
-Yeah. The difference is. I'm gonna win.

444
00:32:21.416 --> 00:32:22.958
-Bye.
-[Matías] Wow.

445
00:32:23.041 --> 00:32:24.458
-Bye.
-[Viviana] Let's go.

446
00:32:24.541 --> 00:32:27.416
-I want to see you at the house by 9:00.
-See you Monday!

447
00:32:29.833 --> 00:32:31.375
How did you get my number?

448
00:32:32.541 --> 00:32:35.708
The receptionist.
I need to be able to contact my boss.

449
00:32:38.625 --> 00:32:39.625
Hmm.

450
00:32:49.666 --> 00:32:51.125
[Lucero exhales]

451
00:32:55.583 --> 00:32:57.000
[giggles]

452
00:32:59.458 --> 00:33:02.375
["¿Quieres Ser Mi Amante?"
[by Camilo Sesto playing]

453
00:33:24.083 --> 00:33:25.458
Do you come to this place often?

454
00:33:26.208 --> 00:33:27.791
[giggles]

455
00:33:27.875 --> 00:33:28.916
No.

456
00:33:29.000 --> 00:33:30.041
No?

457
00:33:31.083 --> 00:33:32.750
-[Lucero] Do you?
-[Matías laughs]

458
00:33:32.833 --> 00:33:34.375
Do you do this often?

459
00:33:35.291 --> 00:33:36.875
[Matías] Go out with my students' moms?

460
00:33:41.166 --> 00:33:42.333
[Matías exhales]

461
00:33:46.958 --> 00:33:50.458
Nah. I don't do that. Ever.

462
00:33:51.083 --> 00:33:52.541
I'm new to this.

463
00:33:54.916 --> 00:33:58.000
And I've had opportunities. Really.

464
00:34:01.083 --> 00:34:02.500
But you're different.

465
00:34:06.708 --> 00:34:09.416
Wow. You're pretty direct. aren't you?

466
00:34:31.958 --> 00:34:35.625
Don't you think when you're honest.
people open up to you?

467
00:34:39.166 --> 00:34:40.625
-Maybe.
-Mm-hmm.

468
00:34:43.250 --> 00:34:44.875
[breathing deeply]

469
00:34:54.333 --> 00:34:56.041
[Lucero breathes deeply]

470
00:34:56.125 --> 00:34:57.833
Why did you bring me here?

471
00:35:20.958 --> 00:35:24.541
[breathing heavily]

472
00:35:34.625 --> 00:35:38.000
[breathing heavily]

473
00:35:38.083 --> 00:35:40.083
[moaning]

474
00:35:41.041 --> 00:35:43.041
[music fades]

475
00:35:46.583 --> 00:35:49.125
-You're beautiful. Beautiful.
-[music turns suspenseful]

476
00:35:49.208 --> 00:35:50.416
Beautiful.

477
00:35:51.208 --> 00:35:53.541
You're beautiful. Beautiful.

478
00:35:54.416 --> 00:35:56.916
[breathing heavily]

479
00:36:06.875 --> 00:36:08.875
[Lucero moans]

480
00:36:11.083 --> 00:36:14.791
[continues moaning]

481
00:36:18.000 --> 00:36:19.125
[moans]

482
00:36:21.458 --> 00:36:23.458
[music fades]

483
00:36:25.041 --> 00:36:28.750
[echoing moans]

484
00:36:48.333 --> 00:36:50.333
[tense pulsing music playing]

485
00:36:56.541 --> 00:36:57.833
[Matías] Number four.

486
00:36:58.500 --> 00:36:59.916
Chin up.

487
00:37:00.000 --> 00:37:02.041
Number three. Go.

488
00:37:02.125 --> 00:37:03.041
Chin up!

489
00:37:03.125 --> 00:37:05.000
Number two. Ready.

490
00:37:05.500 --> 00:37:07.875
Viviana. don't forget. Your feet. Loose.

491
00:37:07.958 --> 00:37:09.750
Yes? That's it.

492
00:37:09.833 --> 00:37:11.000
Number one.

493
00:37:12.750 --> 00:37:15.750
Okay. everybody. Ready!

494
00:37:16.583 --> 00:37:17.583
-Go.
-[beep]

495
00:37:19.875 --> 00:37:21.041
That's it! More. more. more.

496
00:37:21.125 --> 00:37:23.083
Faster. Faster. Faster.
Very good. Viviana.

497
00:37:23.875 --> 00:37:25.875
M. I'M OUT IN 30. YOU IN?

498
00:37:25.958 --> 00:37:27.375
M. I'M DYING TO SEE YOU.

499
00:37:28.291 --> 00:37:29.458
[indistinct chatter]

500
00:37:30.416 --> 00:37:31.416
[Matías] Very good.

501
00:37:31.500 --> 00:37:33.916
[suspenseful music playing]

502
00:37:34.000 --> 00:37:34.875
Viviana.

503
00:37:34.958 --> 00:37:37.666
[Matías continues indistinctly]

504
00:37:37.750 --> 00:37:38.750
That's it. Farther.

505
00:37:44.958 --> 00:37:48.083
-[Cristian] Yes?
-Cris. how's my schedule today?

506
00:37:50.250 --> 00:37:52.416
[Cristian] Uh… it's packed.

507
00:37:54.375 --> 00:37:56.708
Cancel everything. Would you. please?

508
00:37:56.791 --> 00:38:00.416
-Yes. yes. Yes. You'll see.
-[woman] I'm sure I will.

509
00:38:00.500 --> 00:38:02.460
-He's coming.
-[Matías] Girls. good session today.

510
00:38:02.541 --> 00:38:04.208
-Thank you.
-You're superstars.

511
00:38:07.916 --> 00:38:09.541
[girls] Whoo!

512
00:38:09.625 --> 00:38:11.500
[laughs] Oh my God!

513
00:38:11.583 --> 00:38:13.541
-It's so obvious. dude!
-Stop it!

514
00:38:13.625 --> 00:38:16.666
God. you're drooling all over him.
[laughs]

515
00:38:16.750 --> 00:38:18.083
["Hoy Tengo Ganas de Ti" playing]

516
00:38:18.166 --> 00:38:19.958
Do you like flowers? Do you?

517
00:38:20.041 --> 00:38:21.250
-I love them.
-Yeah?

518
00:38:21.333 --> 00:38:22.958
-Mm-hmm.
-[chuckles]

519
00:38:23.458 --> 00:38:25.166
-Are you lying?
-[giggles]

520
00:38:25.250 --> 00:38:27.125
-You don't like them?
-[both laugh]

521
00:38:27.208 --> 00:38:29.916
You don't. [laughs]

522
00:38:30.916 --> 00:38:32.836
-You really don't like them.
-[laughing] I don't.

523
00:38:32.875 --> 00:38:34.708
[laughing] Oh. shit.

524
00:38:35.208 --> 00:38:38.625
-Oh…
-[laughs]

525
00:38:40.708 --> 00:38:43.500
["Hoy Tengo Ganas de Ti" continues]

526
00:38:57.291 --> 00:39:00.291
[Matías] Is there something
you've always wanted to do?

527
00:39:03.708 --> 00:39:06.583
[laughs] What's that look?

528
00:39:06.666 --> 00:39:07.916
Huh?

529
00:39:10.833 --> 00:39:11.833
Come.

530
00:39:26.000 --> 00:39:28.541
[sultry music playing]

531
00:39:31.916 --> 00:39:32.916
[Lucero moans]

532
00:39:36.958 --> 00:39:38.500
[moaning]

533
00:39:42.916 --> 00:39:44.833
[breathing heavily]

534
00:39:44.916 --> 00:39:48.791
[both moaning]

535
00:39:48.875 --> 00:39:50.375
[music fades]

536
00:40:06.625 --> 00:40:10.750
[Miguel] Cheers to the most brilliant
and badass lawyer in Mexico.

537
00:40:10.833 --> 00:40:12.791
-[Lucero giggles]
-[Miguel] Really. Lucero.

538
00:40:13.583 --> 00:40:15.750
Today. me. Tomorrow. you.

539
00:40:15.833 --> 00:40:17.041
[Lucero chuckles softly]

540
00:40:17.125 --> 00:40:18.125
Salud.

541
00:40:19.666 --> 00:40:20.916
Representing people like you

542
00:40:21.000 --> 00:40:23.416
is what gives lawyers
such a bad reputation.

543
00:40:23.500 --> 00:40:25.625
-It's definitely one reason. huh?
-Yeah. yeah. yeah.

544
00:40:25.708 --> 00:40:27.291
Sorry. I'll be right back.

545
00:40:31.375 --> 00:40:33.833
[door slides shut]

546
00:40:33.916 --> 00:40:36.375
[Miguel sighs and sniffles]

547
00:40:36.916 --> 00:40:37.916
Hey. uh…

548
00:40:40.541 --> 00:40:42.000
Did you feel bad?

549
00:40:42.708 --> 00:40:43.708
[Miguel] Hmm?

550
00:40:47.291 --> 00:40:49.750
[exhales] I mean…

551
00:40:49.833 --> 00:40:53.166
When does it become a… miscalculation?

552
00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:55.125
You didn't.

553
00:40:57.041 --> 00:40:59.333
[Miguel chuckles] You did.

554
00:41:03.541 --> 00:41:04.625
[Miguel chuckles]

555
00:41:05.125 --> 00:41:07.000
No. no. no. It's not like that.

556
00:41:07.083 --> 00:41:09.403
The reason I'm asking
is because I'm researching your case.

557
00:41:09.916 --> 00:41:11.958
And who is being investigated?

558
00:41:13.708 --> 00:41:16.291
No. no. You can't stop now.

559
00:41:16.375 --> 00:41:18.791
-You have to tell me.
-[door slides open]

560
00:41:18.875 --> 00:41:20.666
[Lucero clears throat]

561
00:41:25.708 --> 00:41:27.541
-[Fernando] More tequila?
-[Miguel] Mm-hmm.

562
00:41:27.625 --> 00:41:29.291
-[Fernando] Here you go.
-[Miguel] Hmm.

563
00:41:31.125 --> 00:41:33.005
-[Fernando] Want some. babe?
-[Lucero] I'm good.

564
00:41:33.083 --> 00:41:34.083
[Fernando] Mm.

565
00:41:34.958 --> 00:41:36.208
[knocking]

566
00:41:36.291 --> 00:41:37.583
[Viviana] Matías. hey.

567
00:41:37.666 --> 00:41:39.291
-Viviana. hello.
-Can I come in?

568
00:41:39.375 --> 00:41:40.708
[Matías] Yes. please.

569
00:41:42.458 --> 00:41:45.500
[Viviana] Um. I wanted to ask you if…

570
00:41:46.541 --> 00:41:48.791
If you think we could…

571
00:41:49.625 --> 00:41:50.458
[Matías] Yeah?

572
00:41:50.541 --> 00:41:53.184
If you think we could put in
some extra hours together or something.

573
00:41:53.208 --> 00:41:55.166
because I think we're a good team and…

574
00:41:55.250 --> 00:41:56.541
-[Matías] Uh.
-I… don't know.

575
00:41:56.625 --> 00:41:59.166
Uh… Sure. We can. We can. How about…

576
00:41:59.250 --> 00:42:03.875
It's just I'm really grateful for you.
You're… the best coach I've ever had.

577
00:42:03.958 --> 00:42:04.875
-Yeah?
-Yes.

578
00:42:04.958 --> 00:42:06.791
-Thanks a lot.
-No. thank you.

579
00:42:06.875 --> 00:42:09.208
Mm... Viviana. no. I'm sorry.

580
00:42:09.291 --> 00:42:10.625
-None of that.
-Oh. I'm sorry.

581
00:42:10.708 --> 00:42:12.208
No. no. it's fine. but don't...

582
00:42:12.291 --> 00:42:14.125
-I'm an idiot.
-Stop. stop. stop!

583
00:42:14.208 --> 00:42:15.625
Come on. It's fine.

584
00:42:16.125 --> 00:42:17.250
See you tomorrow.

585
00:42:21.333 --> 00:42:23.083
[exterior door closes]

586
00:42:23.166 --> 00:42:25.500
[tense music playing]

587
00:42:30.666 --> 00:42:32.416
[elevator bell rings]

588
00:42:53.833 --> 00:42:55.500
[exhales]

589
00:42:55.583 --> 00:42:57.583
[heavy metal playing on headphones]

590
00:43:19.750 --> 00:43:21.666
[door closes]

591
00:43:21.750 --> 00:43:24.666
[Fernando] I just walked in the door.
Yeah. it's great that you called.

592
00:43:24.750 --> 00:43:27.208
I was going to call you
and let you know that next week

593
00:43:27.291 --> 00:43:30.166
we need to do maintenance on the pool
and a couple of machines.

594
00:43:30.250 --> 00:43:32.375
So… so. we have to reschedule.

595
00:43:32.958 --> 00:43:34.041
Most of...

596
00:43:34.125 --> 00:43:35.291
What?

597
00:43:38.750 --> 00:43:39.750
What?

598
00:43:43.000 --> 00:43:45.000
Uh… What are you talking about?

599
00:43:52.500 --> 00:43:55.000
Are you fucking with me. Matías?
Is this a joke?

600
00:43:56.041 --> 00:43:58.041
[tense music continues]

601
00:43:59.125 --> 00:44:02.333
No. no. no. no.
Where are you? I'm on my way.

602
00:44:03.666 --> 00:44:04.750
Where…

603
00:44:06.250 --> 00:44:07.416
Matías.

604
00:44:10.375 --> 00:44:12.041
[music fades]

605
00:44:15.833 --> 00:44:18.375
[door opens and closes]

606
00:44:28.583 --> 00:44:30.166
Where were you?

607
00:44:30.250 --> 00:44:33.333
[Matías] I was going to shower
but I missed you too much.

608
00:44:53.125 --> 00:44:55.125
[Matías breathes deeply]

609
00:44:57.958 --> 00:44:59.958
[exhales]

610
00:45:08.125 --> 00:45:09.750
You don't have to say it.

611
00:45:11.208 --> 00:45:13.458
But I know if it's good for me.

612
00:45:14.666 --> 00:45:15.958
and it is.

613
00:45:17.458 --> 00:45:19.416
then I know you feel it too.

614
00:45:22.416 --> 00:45:24.083
Not necessarily.

615
00:45:32.041 --> 00:45:33.166
[cell phone buzzes]

616
00:45:41.291 --> 00:45:42.333
[exhales]

617
00:45:45.208 --> 00:45:46.208
[cell phone chimes]

618
00:45:51.083 --> 00:45:52.166
[Lucero] Hey.

619
00:45:55.750 --> 00:45:58.833
But I've never come
so many times in my life.

620
00:46:02.666 --> 00:46:04.000
[Matías exhales]

621
00:46:05.583 --> 00:46:08.125
[sultry music playing]

622
00:46:27.416 --> 00:46:31.708
[Lucero breathes heavily]

623
00:46:37.958 --> 00:46:40.250
[moaning]

624
00:46:48.041 --> 00:46:50.083
[Lucero moans]

625
00:46:50.166 --> 00:46:52.500
[sultry music continues]

626
00:46:57.333 --> 00:46:59.333
[moaning]

627
00:47:22.250 --> 00:47:24.333
[moaning]

628
00:47:35.166 --> 00:47:36.041
[music fades]

629
00:47:36.125 --> 00:47:37.750
[Matías] I have to tell you something.

630
00:47:37.833 --> 00:47:39.875
I've never felt this way
about anyone before.

631
00:47:40.916 --> 00:47:42.291
Seriously.

632
00:47:42.375 --> 00:47:44.875
I don't really need a boyfriend.
I'm married.

633
00:47:44.958 --> 00:47:47.125
[giggles]

634
00:47:50.000 --> 00:47:51.250
You're gonna break my heart.

635
00:47:56.333 --> 00:47:57.333
Hmm?

636
00:48:04.291 --> 00:48:06.041
I lied to you. I'm sorry.

637
00:48:09.750 --> 00:48:10.750
Yeah.

638
00:48:12.041 --> 00:48:14.916
I didn't stop competing
because of my injury.

639
00:48:19.666 --> 00:48:22.083
I stopped competing because the…

640
00:48:24.708 --> 00:48:30.791
The doctor prescribed me some pills that
were supposed to help with the injury.

641
00:48:32.458 --> 00:48:34.083
and I became addicted.

642
00:48:36.875 --> 00:48:38.166
Stupid.

643
00:48:45.416 --> 00:48:47.250
Basically ruined my life.

644
00:48:50.250 --> 00:48:51.750
I lost everything.

645
00:49:03.791 --> 00:49:05.541
But I wouldn't change a thing.

646
00:49:07.333 --> 00:49:09.958
Because everything I've done
has brought me here to you.

647
00:49:10.833 --> 00:49:12.041
[sighs]

648
00:49:12.916 --> 00:49:14.958
[soft dramatic music playing]

649
00:49:15.041 --> 00:49:17.375
And there's nowhere else I'd rather be.

650
00:49:20.666 --> 00:49:22.125
I love you.

651
00:49:22.208 --> 00:49:23.750
[music intensifies]

652
00:49:23.833 --> 00:49:24.708
[kisses]

653
00:49:24.791 --> 00:49:27.375
[Matías sighs]

654
00:49:31.791 --> 00:49:33.791
[sobbing]

655
00:49:41.041 --> 00:49:43.041
[exhaling]

656
00:49:46.625 --> 00:49:48.041
[sobbing]

657
00:49:49.083 --> 00:49:50.333
[Lucero] Baby?

658
00:49:50.416 --> 00:49:52.333
[Viviana] Nothing's wrong. Mom.

659
00:49:52.416 --> 00:49:53.583
Viviana?

660
00:49:54.125 --> 00:49:55.541
[Viviana] I'm fine.

661
00:49:58.083 --> 00:49:59.458
[Lucero] What's wrong?

662
00:50:00.500 --> 00:50:02.580
-[Viviana] It's nothing. it's stupid.
-[Julián] Here.

663
00:50:02.625 --> 00:50:05.333
-Drink this.
-[Lucero] That doesn't matter. Tell me.

664
00:50:06.500 --> 00:50:07.500
Mmm?

665
00:50:10.416 --> 00:50:11.958
Why won't you tell me?

666
00:50:12.041 --> 00:50:14.208
Vivi. you have to tell her.

667
00:50:14.750 --> 00:50:15.833
[Lucero] What?

668
00:50:17.583 --> 00:50:18.916
[door opens]

669
00:50:19.000 --> 00:50:20.916
[Fernando] Lucero? Are you home. babe?

670
00:50:21.000 --> 00:50:22.166
One minute.

671
00:50:26.333 --> 00:50:28.291
It's not serious. Mom.

672
00:50:28.375 --> 00:50:31.125
Please don't tell Dad.
I don't want him to worry.

673
00:50:31.208 --> 00:50:33.916
It's just training stuff. It's nothing.

674
00:50:34.541 --> 00:50:36.083
Don't worry. I won't.

675
00:50:43.958 --> 00:50:47.500
I want you to know
that I will always. always.

676
00:50:48.041 --> 00:50:49.375
always be there for you.

677
00:50:51.083 --> 00:50:53.541
You are the most important things to me.

678
00:50:53.625 --> 00:50:54.791
Okay?

679
00:50:56.708 --> 00:50:58.666
Go to sleep. It's very late.

680
00:51:11.750 --> 00:51:13.916
Don't even think about telling Mom.

681
00:51:16.958 --> 00:51:17.958
[Fernando] Hey.

682
00:51:29.750 --> 00:51:31.041
[gentle music playing]

683
00:51:32.666 --> 00:51:34.333
You were out late again.

684
00:51:36.166 --> 00:51:37.250
Yeah.

685
00:51:38.000 --> 00:51:39.250
I'm sorry.

686
00:51:43.875 --> 00:51:45.583
You want to tell me anything?

687
00:51:49.583 --> 00:51:50.583
No.

688
00:51:55.583 --> 00:51:56.583
You?

689
00:52:01.083 --> 00:52:02.416
No.

690
00:52:03.541 --> 00:52:05.375
This is not a discussion.

691
00:52:06.333 --> 00:52:10.083
No. No. that's not how things work!
Period. end of story.

692
00:52:12.375 --> 00:52:13.958
-Who was that?
-It's just work.

693
00:52:14.041 --> 00:52:15.708
-Who?
-It's my work. it's my job.

694
00:52:15.791 --> 00:52:18.125
-What's it matter?
-Dad! What's wrong with you?

695
00:52:18.208 --> 00:52:20.458
[tense music playing]

696
00:52:22.083 --> 00:52:25.291
[cell phone buzzes]

697
00:52:25.375 --> 00:52:26.583
[Lucero] What happened?

698
00:52:29.166 --> 00:52:32.500
M. SEE YOU TONIGHT?

699
00:52:32.583 --> 00:52:34.291
Julián. what happened?

700
00:52:34.375 --> 00:52:37.666
M. I NEED TO TALK TO YOU. IT'S IMPORTANT

701
00:52:37.750 --> 00:52:40.250
M. YOU DRIVE ME CRAZY. I NEED YOU!

702
00:52:43.416 --> 00:52:45.458
I need you to keep your mouth shut.

703
00:52:46.291 --> 00:52:48.250
-Got it?
-Ah! [laughs]

704
00:52:48.333 --> 00:52:49.375
What was that?

705
00:52:49.458 --> 00:52:51.958
That's for everything
you make me do in there.

706
00:52:52.041 --> 00:52:54.291
-But I'm paying you!
-Oh. shut up.

707
00:52:54.916 --> 00:52:57.625
CORTINA LAW

708
00:52:57.708 --> 00:52:59.958
-[attorney] We want the house.
-Agreed.

709
00:53:01.125 --> 00:53:02.445
[attorney] And the vacation home.

710
00:53:03.750 --> 00:53:06.000
No. That's his family's home.

711
00:53:06.083 --> 00:53:07.625
[attorney] Then what's on the table?

712
00:53:08.583 --> 00:53:09.791
The proposal we gave you.

713
00:53:11.083 --> 00:53:13.166
-That's our final offer.
-[Miguel chuckles]

714
00:53:13.250 --> 00:53:14.250
Impressive. Cortina.

715
00:53:15.750 --> 00:53:18.416
[attorney] Don't worry. Malena.
We're going to fight for it.

716
00:53:20.875 --> 00:53:22.416
[Miguel] Okay… [clears throat]

717
00:53:23.708 --> 00:53:25.083
I've got to run.

718
00:53:27.083 --> 00:53:30.041
Lucero. thank you very much.

719
00:53:36.125 --> 00:53:37.375
I'll see you tomorrow.

720
00:53:38.500 --> 00:53:39.791
[Lucero] Okay.

721
00:53:40.791 --> 00:53:42.166
Goodbye. Malena.

722
00:53:42.833 --> 00:53:44.000
Lucero.

723
00:53:45.208 --> 00:53:47.833
Give me a moment. Just sit next to me.

724
00:53:55.875 --> 00:53:58.541
Malena. I already said no.

725
00:53:59.333 --> 00:54:01.458
I'm doing my job. I'm sorry.

726
00:54:01.541 --> 00:54:04.250
It's okay. I believe you. Hm.

727
00:54:06.083 --> 00:54:07.208
ÁVILA LAW ATTORNEYS

728
00:54:07.291 --> 00:54:08.541
[Lucero] What's this?

729
00:54:09.166 --> 00:54:10.333
REFORMA HOTEL

730
00:54:10.916 --> 00:54:12.458
That's my offer.

731
00:54:32.250 --> 00:54:35.000
-[phone chimes]
-[Lucero exhales]

732
00:54:35.083 --> 00:54:37.625
[tense music playing]

733
00:54:48.083 --> 00:54:49.083
[music fades]

734
00:54:49.875 --> 00:54:52.375
["El Recuento de los Daños"
by Gloria Trevi playing]

735
00:54:52.458 --> 00:54:55.291
You know what I was thinking
when we first met at the the pool

736
00:54:55.375 --> 00:54:57.666
when I felt my heart race? [grunts]

737
00:54:57.750 --> 00:55:01.500
I feel like that happened a century ago.
you know?

738
00:55:01.583 --> 00:55:03.500
-It's felt like. forever...
-Listen. Matías.

739
00:55:03.583 --> 00:55:05.463
-I go crazy if I don't see you.
-Matías. Listen.

740
00:55:05.500 --> 00:55:07.851
-I'll call you 12 times and...
-I need to tell you something.

741
00:55:07.875 --> 00:55:08.791
What?

742
00:55:08.875 --> 00:55:10.416
We can't see each other anymore.

743
00:55:10.500 --> 00:55:12.208
Woah. woah. woah. Uh…

744
00:55:13.541 --> 00:55:16.041
-I know that…
-What do you mean we can't see each other?

745
00:55:16.125 --> 00:55:20.083
This was supposed to be something fun
and light for both. It's not anymore.

746
00:55:20.166 --> 00:55:22.416
-This has to stop.
-Are you kidding me?

747
00:55:22.500 --> 00:55:24.166
-Are you joking?
-No.

748
00:55:25.041 --> 00:55:26.958
No. Look.

749
00:55:30.333 --> 00:55:32.708
It was amazing being with you.

750
00:55:34.000 --> 00:55:35.666
But we can't be together.

751
00:55:41.250 --> 00:55:43.708
-Because of Fernando.
-No.

752
00:55:43.791 --> 00:55:45.083
Yes.

753
00:55:45.166 --> 00:55:48.750
Lucero. I know your life is fucking shit
and you want to get out of there.

754
00:55:48.833 --> 00:55:51.583
-I know perfectly well.
-What do you know about my life?

755
00:55:51.666 --> 00:55:53.226
-I know.
-You don't because we just met.

756
00:55:53.291 --> 00:55:56.041
-You don't know me at all.
-I know that you're perfect for me.

757
00:55:56.125 --> 00:55:58.476
You think I don't know you?
That I'm a kid. that I'm stupid?

758
00:55:58.500 --> 00:56:01.041
I know you perfectly well.
You've told me with your eyes.

759
00:56:01.125 --> 00:56:04.458
No. that's just shit
I thought you wanted to hear in bed.

760
00:56:06.166 --> 00:56:07.625
[Matías exclaims]

761
00:56:08.375 --> 00:56:11.041
-Wait. listen.
-Wait. Wait. wait. Wait. Wait a minute.

762
00:56:11.125 --> 00:56:12.125
Look at me. Look at me.

763
00:56:12.208 --> 00:56:14.541
-Okay.
-Yes. look at me.

764
00:56:14.625 --> 00:56:15.750
I mean. it was fun.

765
00:56:16.791 --> 00:56:18.541
But it's over.

766
00:56:18.625 --> 00:56:20.416
We can't be together.

767
00:56:21.291 --> 00:56:23.500
-That's not true.
-Goodbye.

768
00:56:35.000 --> 00:56:36.833
[music fades]

769
00:56:36.916 --> 00:56:39.375
[gentle music playing]

770
00:56:41.041 --> 00:56:42.458
[door opens]

771
00:57:03.166 --> 00:57:05.208
[gentle music continues]

772
00:57:18.291 --> 00:57:19.500
What do you think?

773
00:57:20.583 --> 00:57:23.875
[attorney] What can I say. Lucero?
It's everything we asked for.

774
00:57:23.958 --> 00:57:26.250
Yes. it's the complete package.

775
00:57:26.333 --> 00:57:28.041
It seemed fair to us.

776
00:57:29.333 --> 00:57:31.041
[attorney] Well. I think it's great.

777
00:57:31.125 --> 00:57:32.605
I'll have to bring this to my client.

778
00:57:32.666 --> 00:57:36.375
but I think she will be
very pleased with this offer.

779
00:57:36.458 --> 00:57:38.833
Yeah. I'll do the same.

780
00:57:40.375 --> 00:57:42.625
And… [clears throat] …well.

781
00:57:44.333 --> 00:57:46.625
I trust that with this adjustment.

782
00:57:46.708 --> 00:57:48.541
any standing animosity is resolved.

783
00:57:48.625 --> 00:57:52.083
[cell phone buzzes]

784
00:57:56.541 --> 00:57:57.375
[exhales]

785
00:57:57.458 --> 00:58:00.958
[Miguel] Lucero. who the hell
authorized giving everything to Malena?

786
00:58:01.041 --> 00:58:03.416
Pick up the fucking phone!
This isn't over.

787
00:58:03.500 --> 00:58:05.833
You better fucking call me back.

788
00:58:05.916 --> 00:58:07.791
-[Cristian] Sorry for interrupting.
-It's fine.

789
00:58:07.875 --> 00:58:10.351
-Uh. your client is here.
-[Lucero] I'm not expecting a client.

790
00:58:10.375 --> 00:58:13.000
-Then should I have him wait?
-You see?

791
00:58:13.833 --> 00:58:15.375
I'll handle this. Cristian. thank you.

792
00:58:15.458 --> 00:58:17.916
-Just close the door. please.
-[Cristian] Sure.

793
00:58:18.000 --> 00:58:19.000
Hey.

794
00:58:19.750 --> 00:58:22.125
-[door closes]
-[Matías] I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

795
00:58:22.208 --> 00:58:24.088
-What are you doing here?
-I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

796
00:58:24.166 --> 00:58:25.875
-I needed to see you.
-You can't come here.

797
00:58:25.958 --> 00:58:29.291
-It's just... You weren't answering me.
-Don't ever come here. You have to leave!

798
00:58:29.375 --> 00:58:32.083
Don't worry. don't worry.
No one saw me. I'll go now. okay?

799
00:58:32.166 --> 00:58:34.250
-Matías. I was very clear.
-Yes.

800
00:58:34.333 --> 00:58:36.958
Yes. you were. That's why I want to talk.
You're absolutely right.

801
00:58:37.041 --> 00:58:38.291
You're absolutely right.

802
00:58:41.791 --> 00:58:42.875
I've been up all night.

803
00:58:42.958 --> 00:58:46.208
I haven't been able to sleep at all
thinking about what you said yesterday…

804
00:58:46.291 --> 00:58:47.750
-And you're totally right.
-[sighs]

805
00:58:47.833 --> 00:58:49.166
Absolutely right.

806
00:58:49.958 --> 00:58:52.726
It's not what we planned. You were
clear about that from the beginning.

807
00:58:52.750 --> 00:58:54.375
-You're totally right.
-Yeah.

808
00:58:54.458 --> 00:58:57.250
So. what do we do now?
Because I… love you so much. Lucero.

809
00:58:57.333 --> 00:59:00.750
-[Lucero] Oh. please!
-I mean it. I love with all of my heart.

810
00:59:01.500 --> 00:59:02.708
Listen to me.

811
00:59:03.541 --> 00:59:04.958
-We are no more.
-Don't say that.

812
00:59:05.041 --> 00:59:05.875
-No.
-This is love.

813
00:59:05.958 --> 00:59:08.125
-I know it is.
-You are a child. Leave me alone.

814
00:59:08.208 --> 00:59:11.000
I'm a child? Don't fuck with me.
Do you know what love is?

815
00:59:11.083 --> 00:59:14.458
Does your fucking husband know?
You're saying that I'm a child?

816
00:59:14.541 --> 00:59:16.666
Stay away from my husband.
do you understand?

817
00:59:16.750 --> 00:59:18.833
-No. I don't... I won't.
-Don't mess with my family.

818
00:59:20.833 --> 00:59:22.875
[Matías] Your husband
is already involved in this.

819
00:59:22.958 --> 00:59:25.583
He got himself involved. Look.

820
00:59:25.666 --> 00:59:26.708
Look at my fucking phone!

821
00:59:27.500 --> 00:59:28.625
Take a look!

822
00:59:28.708 --> 00:59:30.625
Lucero. your husband has a fucked up mind.

823
00:59:30.708 --> 00:59:34.500
Look. look. He's got the cash
to pay for his dirty fantasies.

824
00:59:34.583 --> 00:59:36.416
Look! Look at what he asked me to do.

825
00:59:37.291 --> 00:59:39.166
-You recorded us?
-No. not me!

826
00:59:39.250 --> 00:59:41.970
-You gonna show him? Is this a threat?
-He paid me for the recording!

827
00:59:42.000 --> 00:59:45.125
He has been aware of where we are
and everything we were doing all along!

828
00:59:45.208 --> 00:59:47.833
[tense music playing]

829
00:59:50.000 --> 00:59:53.416
But I told him I can't do it anymore.
because I wanted it to be real.

830
00:59:53.500 --> 00:59:55.250
-Because I really love you.
-Let go of me!

831
00:59:55.833 --> 00:59:58.017
-Don't touch me!
-I already broke off the deal with him.

832
00:59:58.041 --> 00:59:59.541
Get out of here. Cristian!

833
00:59:59.625 --> 01:00:01.583
-Cristian!
-Wait. Lucero. Lucero!

834
01:00:01.666 --> 01:00:05.625
[shaking] Lucero. please. please.
Calm down. Fuck. no.

835
01:00:05.708 --> 01:00:07.750
-Stop. The deal is off now. please.
-[door opens]

836
01:00:07.833 --> 01:00:08.875
Get out.

837
01:00:09.750 --> 01:00:13.125
-[Cristian] Uh. I'm sorry. you have to go.
-Yeah. yeah!

838
01:00:16.208 --> 01:00:17.708
I'm leaving. okay?

839
01:00:17.791 --> 01:00:18.791
I'm leaving.

840
01:00:19.791 --> 01:00:21.541
It's okay. Cris.

841
01:00:23.708 --> 01:00:25.041
[Cristian] Excuse me.

842
01:00:25.708 --> 01:00:27.208
-[exhales]
-[door closes]

843
01:00:27.291 --> 01:00:29.125
[tense music continues]

844
01:00:29.208 --> 01:00:31.833
[breathing rapidly]

845
01:00:33.541 --> 01:00:36.875
[sobbing]

846
01:00:36.958 --> 01:00:37.958
[music fades]

847
01:00:41.250 --> 01:00:42.416
[Fernando] Hey.

848
01:00:45.666 --> 01:00:46.666
[sniffles]

849
01:00:48.291 --> 01:00:49.375
[exhales]

850
01:00:51.166 --> 01:00:52.375
You all right?

851
01:00:55.708 --> 01:00:56.708
What's up?

852
01:00:59.416 --> 01:01:01.291
-"What's up?"
-[Fernando] Mm-hmm.

853
01:01:02.333 --> 01:01:04.958
Are you serious? What were you thinking?

854
01:01:05.791 --> 01:01:07.875
You should have just saved your money!

855
01:01:07.958 --> 01:01:10.125
If I had known you were
into that sort of thing.

856
01:01:10.208 --> 01:01:12.000
I would have just let you watch!

857
01:01:13.250 --> 01:01:15.291
Why didn't you just ask me?

858
01:01:15.375 --> 01:01:18.958
Instead. you just paid
the first asshole you could think of?

859
01:01:20.000 --> 01:01:22.000
[tense music playing]

860
01:01:22.750 --> 01:01:26.000
-I thought it was what you wanted.
-That's bullshit! How would you know that?

861
01:01:26.083 --> 01:01:27.583
Because you told me.

862
01:01:28.250 --> 01:01:30.166
[exhales] I told you?

863
01:01:30.250 --> 01:01:31.708
What do you mean?

864
01:01:32.375 --> 01:01:35.833
At the party. You talked about
wanting to be with other people.

865
01:01:36.750 --> 01:01:38.708
No. no. no. Fernando.

866
01:01:38.791 --> 01:01:40.208
Don't put this on me.

867
01:01:41.541 --> 01:01:43.625
God. I know you perfectly.

868
01:01:44.625 --> 01:01:47.875
And I know the convoluted way
you twist your thoughts around.

869
01:01:47.958 --> 01:01:50.833
to convince yourself
of your own delusions.

870
01:01:51.458 --> 01:01:54.083
I hope you're happy now. Are you?

871
01:01:54.166 --> 01:01:57.041
Did you like your fantasy?
Did you like what you saw?

872
01:02:03.750 --> 01:02:07.791
Look. You had the affair. not me.

873
01:02:07.875 --> 01:02:09.625
Why don't we talk about that?

874
01:02:13.250 --> 01:02:14.416
[sniffles]

875
01:02:22.083 --> 01:02:24.458
I just wanted to be desired again.

876
01:02:38.791 --> 01:02:40.875
I just wanted to make you happy.

877
01:02:43.583 --> 01:02:45.750
Mom. someone's at the door.

878
01:02:46.500 --> 01:02:47.791
[Lucero] For me?

879
01:02:52.083 --> 01:02:53.916
Everything's fine. hmm?

880
01:02:59.583 --> 01:03:01.916
-[Fernando] Who is it?
-The replacement.

881
01:03:07.416 --> 01:03:08.750
[sighs]

882
01:03:12.458 --> 01:03:14.416
[Viviana] Sure.
if my parents are okay with it.

883
01:03:14.500 --> 01:03:17.017
[Matías] I understand.
I just want to show you that I'm serious.

884
01:03:17.041 --> 01:03:19.666
What? Come on.

885
01:03:19.750 --> 01:03:21.333
[Viviana] Mom. look who it is.

886
01:03:21.416 --> 01:03:22.625
Good afternoon.

887
01:03:22.708 --> 01:03:24.708
[tense music playing]

888
01:03:27.000 --> 01:03:28.208
Mom.

889
01:03:30.625 --> 01:03:32.125
[Matías] I brought you some flowers.

890
01:03:32.750 --> 01:03:35.541
They're beautiful.
Thank you so much. Matías.

891
01:03:35.625 --> 01:03:36.916
These are your favorite. right?

892
01:03:37.458 --> 01:03:39.291
-[Matías] Really?
-[Viviana] Thank you.

893
01:03:42.416 --> 01:03:44.208
[Fernando] Matías. hello.

894
01:03:44.291 --> 01:03:45.625
[Matías] Hey. Fernando.

895
01:03:46.833 --> 01:03:47.916
Come here.

896
01:03:48.833 --> 01:03:51.666
You have a wonderful daughter.

897
01:03:52.250 --> 01:03:53.458
Really.

898
01:03:54.958 --> 01:03:58.750
And I wanted to do the right thing
and come here in person.

899
01:03:58.833 --> 01:04:02.750
And ask you directly for your permission
to ask her out on a date.

900
01:04:03.791 --> 01:04:06.291
[Fernando] Oh. I appreciate
the gesture. but. uh…

901
01:04:06.375 --> 01:04:07.208
[exhales]

902
01:04:07.291 --> 01:04:09.500
…I think that is a bit inappropriate.

903
01:04:10.000 --> 01:04:11.000
[Viviana] Inappropriate?

904
01:04:11.833 --> 01:04:14.583
-I get the concern completely.
-How's it inappropriate?

905
01:04:14.666 --> 01:04:16.083
Viviana. he's your coach.

906
01:04:16.166 --> 01:04:18.250
[Viviana] What does that
have to do with anything?

907
01:04:18.333 --> 01:04:20.541
-I don't understand. Who cares?
-Yeah.

908
01:04:21.750 --> 01:04:24.083
[Viviana] Excuse me.
Would you like something to drink?

909
01:04:25.041 --> 01:04:26.791
-Sure.
-Okay. leave your things here.

910
01:04:26.875 --> 01:04:28.875
And I'll see you in the kitchen.

911
01:04:28.958 --> 01:04:30.333
[Matías] Thank you. Viviana.

912
01:04:30.416 --> 01:04:32.875
[tense music continues]

913
01:04:39.666 --> 01:04:40.791
Excuse me.

914
01:04:55.000 --> 01:04:58.666
[Matías] I think the next step is to start
training for four hours in the morning.

915
01:04:58.750 --> 01:05:00.125
Two hours in the afternoon.

916
01:05:00.208 --> 01:05:03.625
I think. especially on weekends.
this is super important.

917
01:05:03.708 --> 01:05:05.628
That's when we have
the entire pool to ourselves.

918
01:05:05.708 --> 01:05:09.166
That's when we'll put in the key hours.
That'll be the difference maker.

919
01:05:09.250 --> 01:05:11.500
-Don't you agree?
-[Viviana] Yes. of course.

920
01:05:11.583 --> 01:05:13.000
[Matías] What do you think?

921
01:05:14.750 --> 01:05:16.916
[tense music continues]

922
01:05:17.916 --> 01:05:20.958
I'm not going to charge you
extra for this. Fernando.

923
01:05:21.041 --> 01:05:23.375
-Don't worry about that.
-[Viviana] That's so sweet.

924
01:05:23.958 --> 01:05:25.708
-Thank you.
-[chuckles]

925
01:05:27.416 --> 01:05:29.083
It's my pleasure.

926
01:05:35.166 --> 01:05:37.006
Well. I know
it's bad luck to do it with water.

927
01:05:37.083 --> 01:05:38.958
but how about a toast?

928
01:05:39.041 --> 01:05:41.083
To… to you. to your family.

929
01:05:41.166 --> 01:05:45.333
and to making me…
making me part… part of the family.

930
01:05:45.416 --> 01:05:46.958
-[slams]
-For real?

931
01:05:47.541 --> 01:05:49.375
-[clinking]
-I told you to stay away from him!

932
01:05:52.916 --> 01:05:54.676
-Matías. can we talk outside?
-[Matías] Yeah.

933
01:05:54.750 --> 01:05:56.208
-Outside now.
-[Matías] Sure.

934
01:05:57.958 --> 01:05:59.166
What's wrong?

935
01:05:59.791 --> 01:06:01.333
Why are you being like this?

936
01:06:01.416 --> 01:06:05.166
If I had known they were gonna be so rude.
I wouldn't have made you stay here. Sorry.

937
01:06:05.250 --> 01:06:07.767
Viviana. please. don't... don't...
Don't worry. I'm here for you.

938
01:06:07.791 --> 01:06:11.041
I don't care. I want us to stop hiding.
That's it. We're going to be fine.

939
01:06:11.125 --> 01:06:13.166
-You know what? Let's go train.
-Okay.

940
01:06:13.250 --> 01:06:15.958
Please.
I know this is difficult to understand.

941
01:06:16.041 --> 01:06:18.625
-Don't touch me. Mom.
-Come on. Let's go.

942
01:06:18.708 --> 01:06:20.541
Bye. Excuse me. okay?

943
01:06:20.625 --> 01:06:22.625
[tense music continues]

944
01:06:26.541 --> 01:06:27.833
[footsteps approach]

945
01:06:29.541 --> 01:06:31.541
[Viviana] What is your problem?

946
01:06:31.625 --> 01:06:33.625
[tense music intensifies]

947
01:06:35.916 --> 01:06:39.750
-I have it all recorded. okay?
-Are you trying to blackmail me. asshole?

948
01:06:40.333 --> 01:06:41.750
Oh. I'm not trying.

949
01:06:42.416 --> 01:06:43.958
-Don't be stupid.
-You don't scare me.

950
01:06:44.708 --> 01:06:45.583
Maybe I should.

951
01:06:45.666 --> 01:06:48.250
[scoffs] You know me very well then.

952
01:06:48.750 --> 01:06:50.041
Viviana. our Uber is here.

953
01:06:50.125 --> 01:06:51.958
I apologize for bothering you.

954
01:06:53.625 --> 01:06:56.083
[tense music continues]

955
01:06:59.708 --> 01:07:01.041
[Matías] Viviana.

956
01:07:08.875 --> 01:07:10.833
[suspenseful music playing]

957
01:07:12.708 --> 01:07:15.000
[Lucero] Don't just stand there!
Do something!

958
01:07:19.500 --> 01:07:20.750
Come on. Julián.

959
01:07:23.791 --> 01:07:26.208
No. no. You stay here. I'll go get her.

960
01:07:26.291 --> 01:07:27.291
[exhales]

961
01:07:38.083 --> 01:07:40.083
[suspenseful music continues]

962
01:07:43.708 --> 01:07:45.416
[music fades]

963
01:07:45.500 --> 01:07:46.416
[hard rock music plays]

964
01:07:46.500 --> 01:07:48.458
ONE DAY LATER

965
01:08:32.041 --> 01:08:33.291
[dishes clinking]

966
01:08:47.291 --> 01:08:48.958
You should probably eat.

967
01:08:49.791 --> 01:08:52.291
I have no appetite. I'm gonna lay down.

968
01:08:53.875 --> 01:08:55.583
I'll get you a drink.

969
01:08:58.750 --> 01:09:00.500
[blender whirring]

970
01:09:09.375 --> 01:09:10.750
[Miguel] Lucero!

971
01:09:10.833 --> 01:09:12.958
[tense music playing]

972
01:09:13.041 --> 01:09:14.208
Miguel.

973
01:09:16.166 --> 01:09:17.833
I meant to call. I'm sorry.

974
01:09:17.916 --> 01:09:19.396
It's not a problem. Don't mention it.

975
01:09:19.458 --> 01:09:22.458
Everyone's very busy these days.
and all sorts of things happen.

976
01:09:22.541 --> 01:09:24.141
-[Lucero] Mm-hm.
-[Fernando] Hey. Miguel.

977
01:09:26.583 --> 01:09:27.750
What brings you here?

978
01:09:29.166 --> 01:09:30.291
I have bad news.

979
01:09:31.666 --> 01:09:34.291
And I came to help however I can.

980
01:09:34.375 --> 01:09:38.416
[Fernando] Thank you for coming.
We're in a delicate situation.

981
01:09:39.000 --> 01:09:42.708
Yes. I understand.
I decided to come and tell you in person.

982
01:09:42.791 --> 01:09:46.375
One of the perks of having friends in
the district attorney's office. I guess.

983
01:09:46.458 --> 01:09:47.875
[Viviana sobbing]

984
01:09:53.250 --> 01:09:55.250
[hard rock music playing on headphones]

985
01:09:56.833 --> 01:09:59.125
[Viviana sobs]

986
01:10:17.958 --> 01:10:20.708
-[Fernando] Matías. can we talk outside?
-Yeah. sure. sure.

987
01:10:21.500 --> 01:10:22.625
What's wrong?

988
01:10:23.291 --> 01:10:25.041
[Viviana] Why are you being like this?

989
01:10:25.125 --> 01:10:29.166
If I knew they were going to be so rude.
I wouldn't have made you stay. I'm sorry.

990
01:10:29.250 --> 01:10:31.250
You know what? Let's go train.

991
01:10:31.333 --> 01:10:34.083
[Lucero] Please.
I know this is difficult to understand.

992
01:10:34.166 --> 01:10:35.750
[Viviana] Don't touch me. Mom.

993
01:10:40.041 --> 01:10:41.208
["Last One Standing" playing]

994
01:10:41.291 --> 01:10:46.500
♪ Last one
I will be the last one ♪

995
01:10:46.583 --> 01:10:47.875
[music ends abruptly]

996
01:10:49.666 --> 01:10:51.375
[Miguel] Well. this morning

997
01:10:51.458 --> 01:10:54.458
we received a call
from the club's security staff

998
01:10:54.541 --> 01:10:57.416
notifying us of the discovery.
and since you are the owners.

999
01:10:57.500 --> 01:10:59.625
you have a direct responsibility.

1000
01:11:03.708 --> 01:11:05.958
Did you spot anything on the cameras?

1001
01:11:06.541 --> 01:11:09.375
[somber music playing]

1002
01:11:26.333 --> 01:11:31.541
LOMAS CLUB

1003
01:11:33.041 --> 01:11:34.333
[music fades]

1004
01:11:34.416 --> 01:11:35.750
-No.
-[cell phone buzzes]

1005
01:11:35.833 --> 01:11:37.791
Apparently. they were turned off.

1006
01:11:38.375 --> 01:11:41.041
[Viviana] Mom. Lucía is calling.
What should I do?

1007
01:11:41.125 --> 01:11:42.458
Answer it.

1008
01:11:45.833 --> 01:11:46.875
Hey. Lucía.

1009
01:11:48.916 --> 01:11:51.625
Yes. I know.
Sorry for not answering before.

1010
01:11:53.833 --> 01:11:55.708
Okay. See you later.

1011
01:11:57.791 --> 01:12:00.101
Okay. Lucía just told me
the parents are going to the club.

1012
01:12:00.125 --> 01:12:02.541
We better go.
We better… reassure the families.

1013
01:12:02.625 --> 01:12:03.458
Yeah. yeah.

1014
01:12:03.541 --> 01:12:07.041
Hold on. We already know that Viviana
was the last person who was with Matías.

1015
01:12:07.125 --> 01:12:09.875
Hey. no. No. no. no.
She had nothing to do with this. okay?

1016
01:12:09.958 --> 01:12:12.208
Okay. relax. Everybody just calm down.

1017
01:12:12.291 --> 01:12:14.601
It's better if I take her
to the District Attorney's office

1018
01:12:14.625 --> 01:12:15.865
before the police come looking.

1019
01:12:15.916 --> 01:12:19.250
Miguel. you must know
that Viviana is innocent.

1020
01:12:19.333 --> 01:12:21.083
Yes. I know. Lucero.

1021
01:12:21.166 --> 01:12:24.625
And I swear
I will do everything I can to protect her.

1022
01:12:26.708 --> 01:12:29.416
Then I'll go to the DA's office
with the two of you.

1023
01:12:30.083 --> 01:12:32.166
You go to the club and I'll go with them.

1024
01:12:32.250 --> 01:12:34.750
[Miguel] To be honest. Lucero.
you shouldn't come.

1025
01:12:34.833 --> 01:12:37.083
If the three of us arrive together.
it'll be suspicious.

1026
01:12:37.166 --> 01:12:39.166
[Lucero sighs] All right.

1027
01:12:39.250 --> 01:12:42.333
My love. it's just protocol.
Don't worry. I'll meet you there.

1028
01:12:43.208 --> 01:12:46.208
-[people clamoring]
-[police sirens blare]

1029
01:12:55.000 --> 01:12:58.958
MEDICAL EXAMINER SERVICE

1030
01:13:03.500 --> 01:13:05.140
[woman 1] Fernando. I'm glad you're here.

1031
01:13:05.166 --> 01:13:09.166
-We've been waiting. Where's Lucero?
-Lucero is at home. She's a little…

1032
01:13:09.250 --> 01:13:12.291
-No. she is… I don't know.
-[woman 1] Okay. okay.

1033
01:13:13.375 --> 01:13:15.583
What happened. Fernando? What's going on?

1034
01:13:15.666 --> 01:13:17.583
Nothing. We don't know anything as far as…

1035
01:13:17.666 --> 01:13:20.226
-[woman 2] How is that possible?
-We don't know. We have to wait.

1036
01:13:20.250 --> 01:13:21.708
-[woman 2] Okay.
-Hi. girls.

1037
01:13:21.791 --> 01:13:22.916
[Lucía] Where's Viviana?

1038
01:13:23.000 --> 01:13:24.708
[murmuring]

1039
01:13:24.791 --> 01:13:27.500
Good morning. Fernando Cortina.
My wife and I are the owners.

1040
01:13:27.583 --> 01:13:31.208
[woman 3] No. he was not a normal guy.
I had a bad feeling about him.

1041
01:13:31.291 --> 01:13:34.208
[woman 4] I guess so.
but he was a good coach. And so young.

1042
01:13:34.291 --> 01:13:36.750
[man] He was just a kid.
It's a horrible thing.

1043
01:13:36.833 --> 01:13:37.916
And so far from home.

1044
01:13:38.000 --> 01:13:39.458
Uh. everyone.

1045
01:13:40.208 --> 01:13:43.833
Calm down. okay? Please.
We... we don't know anything.

1046
01:13:45.500 --> 01:13:47.041
Calm down. please.

1047
01:13:49.125 --> 01:13:51.125
-[line calling]
-[tense music playing]

1048
01:13:51.208 --> 01:13:53.208
[indistinct chatter]

1049
01:13:58.500 --> 01:14:00.458
[line calling]

1050
01:14:13.250 --> 01:14:14.916
[Lucero] Hi. How are you?

1051
01:14:15.000 --> 01:14:17.625
-Have you seen Prosecutor Peña?
-[man] No. he isn't in.

1052
01:14:17.708 --> 01:14:20.500
He was supposed to bring my daughter.
You haven't seen him?

1053
01:14:20.583 --> 01:14:23.791
-[man] No. Not today.
-[Lucero] Okay. thank you.

1054
01:14:25.750 --> 01:14:28.083
I thought we were meeting my mom. Miguel.

1055
01:14:28.666 --> 01:14:31.958
Yes. but first I want you
to eat something.

1056
01:14:32.041 --> 01:14:33.458
Okay? Then we'll go.

1057
01:14:33.541 --> 01:14:35.916
I don't want you to faint
in front of the judge.

1058
01:14:39.291 --> 01:14:41.625
Did you tell my mom that we came here?

1059
01:14:41.708 --> 01:14:44.000
Yes. honey. don't worry about that.

1060
01:14:53.291 --> 01:14:55.041
So. can you tell me what happened?

1061
01:14:57.833 --> 01:14:59.250
I promise I'm innocent.

1062
01:15:00.750 --> 01:15:03.583
But you were there. right?
Just the two of you?

1063
01:15:05.791 --> 01:15:06.791
So?

1064
01:15:13.250 --> 01:15:17.083
He came over and brought flowers.
and he asked me out.

1065
01:15:17.166 --> 01:15:18.416
Mm.

1066
01:15:18.916 --> 01:15:21.000
-I was excited.
-Well. yeah.

1067
01:15:22.833 --> 01:15:25.250
But my parents were not excited at all.

1068
01:15:26.750 --> 01:15:28.458
So we went to the club to train.

1069
01:15:29.958 --> 01:15:31.250
[Miguel] Together?

1070
01:15:34.291 --> 01:15:36.666
[Viviana] We didn't say a word
the entire ride.

1071
01:15:38.750 --> 01:15:42.333
I was really embarrassed about
how my parents had treated him.

1072
01:15:43.458 --> 01:15:46.458
Everything okay? What did she say to you?

1073
01:15:47.416 --> 01:15:49.875
-That I'm fired.
-They fired you?

1074
01:15:50.375 --> 01:15:51.375
Yes.

1075
01:15:52.958 --> 01:15:54.250
Yeah. yeah.

1076
01:15:56.583 --> 01:15:59.166
-I don't know what's the matter.
-Yeah. I'm not sure.

1077
01:15:59.666 --> 01:16:01.000
I'm sorry.

1078
01:16:01.083 --> 01:16:04.041
-I feel super bad about it.
-No. come on.

1079
01:16:04.125 --> 01:16:07.208
There's no need to.
[kisses] It's not your fault.

1080
01:16:08.125 --> 01:16:09.833
Okay? So forget about that.

1081
01:16:11.208 --> 01:16:12.458
Just watch. I'll win them over.

1082
01:16:13.750 --> 01:16:14.750
Okay?

1083
01:16:15.958 --> 01:16:17.291
So don't worry.

1084
01:16:17.375 --> 01:16:19.166
[gentle music playing]

1085
01:16:19.250 --> 01:16:20.666
[sighs]

1086
01:16:21.708 --> 01:16:23.333
I'm gonna fix this.

1087
01:16:25.833 --> 01:16:26.875
[Viviana] Matías!

1088
01:16:28.041 --> 01:16:29.125
Matías!

1089
01:16:29.833 --> 01:16:32.166
-What? What is it?
-The timer.

1090
01:16:32.833 --> 01:16:34.833
Yeah. Okay. are you ready?

1091
01:16:36.666 --> 01:16:38.083
Ready? Go.

1092
01:16:38.166 --> 01:16:40.250
-[stopwatch beeps]
-[splash]

1093
01:16:41.000 --> 01:16:44.583
[Viviana] He started acting really strange
after we got to the club.

1094
01:16:44.666 --> 01:16:45.833
Really strange.

1095
01:16:47.333 --> 01:16:48.625
I don't know.

1096
01:16:48.708 --> 01:16:50.541
Just… weird.

1097
01:16:51.458 --> 01:16:54.041
Like he was drugged.

1098
01:16:56.250 --> 01:17:00.208
And when I got out of the pool.
he was very distracted.

1099
01:17:00.291 --> 01:17:02.166
[tense music playing]

1100
01:17:02.250 --> 01:17:04.583
[Viviana] I asked him
if everything was okay.

1101
01:17:07.000 --> 01:17:10.666
I thought he was angry at me because.
you know. he lost his job because of me.

1102
01:17:10.750 --> 01:17:12.458
What? He was fired?

1103
01:17:13.458 --> 01:17:14.458
Why?

1104
01:17:16.375 --> 01:17:17.416
Tell me.

1105
01:17:19.250 --> 01:17:20.458
You can trust me.

1106
01:17:22.375 --> 01:17:24.000
I had never seen him like that.

1107
01:17:24.083 --> 01:17:26.083
[Viviana panting]

1108
01:17:28.291 --> 01:17:29.750
[Viviana] Who are you texting?

1109
01:17:30.958 --> 01:17:32.416
Tell me!

1110
01:17:33.291 --> 01:17:34.500
Viviana…

1111
01:17:35.083 --> 01:17:37.750
-I don't feel good. Viviana.
-Why are you texting my mom?

1112
01:17:37.833 --> 01:17:40.233
Viviana. I'm not feeling good.
Just give me my phone. please.

1113
01:17:40.916 --> 01:17:42.596
-"Forgive me. I love you"?
-No. no. no. no.

1114
01:17:42.625 --> 01:17:44.625
No. no. no. gimme. gimme. gimme.

1115
01:17:44.708 --> 01:17:47.083
-Give me my phone. dammit!
-No. no. no! Get off!

1116
01:17:47.166 --> 01:17:49.166
-[thud]
-[groans]

1117
01:17:49.250 --> 01:17:51.500
[Matías groaning]

1118
01:17:52.250 --> 01:17:53.250
[Matías] Fuck!

1119
01:17:54.166 --> 01:17:55.750
That's a lot of blood.

1120
01:17:57.458 --> 01:17:59.125
I hit my head hard.

1121
01:17:59.208 --> 01:18:01.416
I really don't feel good.

1122
01:18:02.916 --> 01:18:04.291
[Matías groans]

1123
01:18:04.375 --> 01:18:07.291
-I think I need a doctor.
-Is this real?

1124
01:18:07.375 --> 01:18:09.055
-I hit myself hard.
-What the fuck is this?

1125
01:18:09.125 --> 01:18:10.875
We need to call someone. Give me my phone.

1126
01:18:10.958 --> 01:18:14.625
No. no. no. don't touch me!
Do you think I'm stupid?

1127
01:18:14.708 --> 01:18:18.083
-[groans]
-Did you fuck my mom? That's disgusting!

1128
01:18:18.166 --> 01:18:20.208
[Matías] Your family is disgusting.

1129
01:18:20.291 --> 01:18:23.250
Fuck! It's your shitty family
that's been using me. dammit!

1130
01:18:23.333 --> 01:18:26.541
I want your mother to forgive me. please.
I'm begging you.

1131
01:18:27.666 --> 01:18:29.250
I'm sorry. Viviana.

1132
01:18:29.333 --> 01:18:32.083
Help me. Help me. please.
Call… call… call…

1133
01:18:33.000 --> 01:18:35.458
I think you're pathetic. I hope you die.

1134
01:18:37.250 --> 01:18:39.041
Give me my phone. please.

1135
01:18:39.125 --> 01:18:41.416
[tense music continues]

1136
01:18:47.833 --> 01:18:49.291
[breathing heavily]

1137
01:18:51.666 --> 01:18:53.041
[Fernando] Viviana.

1138
01:18:55.125 --> 01:18:56.875
This is Matías's phone.

1139
01:19:01.458 --> 01:19:02.458
What happened?

1140
01:19:03.125 --> 01:19:05.083
-Are you okay?
-Yes. I'm fine.

1141
01:19:05.833 --> 01:19:07.875
-[sniffles]
-Okay. Hey. no. no.

1142
01:19:07.958 --> 01:19:10.166
-It's okay. sweetheart. Come. it's okay.
-[sobbing]

1143
01:19:12.333 --> 01:19:13.875
Come here.

1144
01:19:16.375 --> 01:19:17.833
[Viviana sobs]

1145
01:19:17.916 --> 01:19:19.208
Sweetheart.

1146
01:19:20.166 --> 01:19:21.000
Look at me.

1147
01:19:21.083 --> 01:19:22.500
[sobbing]

1148
01:19:22.583 --> 01:19:24.208
Wait for me in the car.

1149
01:19:26.375 --> 01:19:28.215
-Don't take long. okay?
-I'll just be a minute.

1150
01:19:28.250 --> 01:19:30.166
It's gonna be fine. Deep breaths.

1151
01:19:35.000 --> 01:19:36.416
[door closes]

1152
01:19:38.000 --> 01:19:40.666
[breathing heavily]

1153
01:19:45.041 --> 01:19:46.333
[groans]

1154
01:19:46.416 --> 01:19:47.958
You disgust me.

1155
01:19:51.125 --> 01:19:54.416
Have you already told… told your daughter
and explained all this shit to her?

1156
01:19:54.500 --> 01:19:57.708
-Because look all this shit you're doing.
-I want you out of here.

1157
01:19:58.375 --> 01:19:59.416
[Matías] What?

1158
01:20:01.500 --> 01:20:03.000
I want you out of here.

1159
01:20:08.583 --> 01:20:11.500
You realize
I don't work for you anymore. right?

1160
01:20:12.541 --> 01:20:14.375
Do you want more money? Is that it?

1161
01:20:14.875 --> 01:20:18.208
I don't want your fucking money!
Relax. I'm not gonna do anything to you.

1162
01:20:20.291 --> 01:20:22.875
Just know every time
your wife closes her eyes.

1163
01:20:22.958 --> 01:20:24.916
I'll be there. fucking her.

1164
01:20:25.000 --> 01:20:26.666
[grunting]

1165
01:20:30.000 --> 01:20:31.083
[Fernando grunts]

1166
01:20:31.166 --> 01:20:33.458
[tense music intensifies]

1167
01:20:33.541 --> 01:20:35.875
[Matías groans]

1168
01:20:39.791 --> 01:20:41.000
[Matías] Asshole.

1169
01:20:41.083 --> 01:20:43.083
[groaning]

1170
01:20:45.125 --> 01:20:47.916
I'll be there. I'll be there.

1171
01:20:48.500 --> 01:20:51.041
[breathing heavily]

1172
01:20:52.041 --> 01:20:53.833
Whenever she closes her eyes…

1173
01:20:57.166 --> 01:20:58.750
I'll be fucking her.

1174
01:21:00.416 --> 01:21:01.916
[breathing heavily]

1175
01:21:02.916 --> 01:21:05.041
[panting]

1176
01:21:05.833 --> 01:21:07.083
[Matías] I'll always…

1177
01:21:08.041 --> 01:21:09.541
I need to see her.

1178
01:21:09.625 --> 01:21:12.583
[sobbing]

1179
01:21:17.583 --> 01:21:18.666
[cell phone buzzes]

1180
01:21:18.750 --> 01:21:21.166
I'm in shock. I can't believe it.

1181
01:21:21.250 --> 01:21:23.250
-[cell phone buzzes]
-Excuse me.

1182
01:21:25.958 --> 01:21:28.083
[Lucero] Miguel. I'm here. Where are you?

1183
01:21:28.166 --> 01:21:31.458
Hey. sorry for not answering.
but I've been busy.

1184
01:21:31.541 --> 01:21:33.625
Busy? Where is my daughter?

1185
01:21:33.708 --> 01:21:37.208
So he was fired before he drowned.

1186
01:21:37.833 --> 01:21:39.500
Oh. poor guy.

1187
01:21:39.583 --> 01:21:41.208
Is this some kind of a threat?

1188
01:21:41.833 --> 01:21:43.916
Give me back my kids.

1189
01:21:44.000 --> 01:21:45.500
What do you want me to do?

1190
01:21:45.583 --> 01:21:47.333
Talk to Malena.

1191
01:21:48.000 --> 01:21:50.000
I'm just asking for what's right.

1192
01:21:53.708 --> 01:21:55.333
[tense music playing]

1193
01:21:55.416 --> 01:21:59.958
OFFICE OF THE ATTORNEY GENERAL

1194
01:22:00.041 --> 01:22:01.583
Malena. it's Lucero.

1195
01:22:03.041 --> 01:22:04.666
Stop. [indistinct]

1196
01:22:04.750 --> 01:22:07.250
POLICE LINE

1197
01:22:14.166 --> 01:22:16.791
[woman] I think you should know
what everyone's talking about.

1198
01:22:16.875 --> 01:22:20.375
I think someone saw Lucero with Matías.
They were together.

1199
01:22:23.958 --> 01:22:25.666
Come on. you can trust me.

1200
01:22:27.541 --> 01:22:31.000
Lucero fired Matías.
That's why they were together.

1201
01:22:31.958 --> 01:22:33.541
But he just got here.

1202
01:22:33.625 --> 01:22:37.125
Yeah. I know.
but he had a problem with drugs.

1203
01:22:37.208 --> 01:22:39.375
That's why he stopped competing in Spain.

1204
01:22:39.458 --> 01:22:42.166
-But why make him the coach then?
-Because I didn't know!

1205
01:22:42.250 --> 01:22:45.000
As soon as we found out.
we fired him. that was the…

1206
01:22:47.750 --> 01:22:49.916
["Me Muero" by La Quinta Estación playing]

1207
01:23:01.416 --> 01:23:02.856
I didn't know what to order for you.

1208
01:23:05.250 --> 01:23:08.041
You guys come here so often
and I don't know why.

1209
01:23:11.500 --> 01:23:12.916
Thanks for coming.

1210
01:23:15.333 --> 01:23:17.291
I can't imagine it was easy.

1211
01:23:17.375 --> 01:23:18.958
You can imagine.

1212
01:23:19.458 --> 01:23:23.625
Isn't this where you decided
to sabotage your family as well?

1213
01:23:24.250 --> 01:23:25.375
What do you want?

1214
01:23:26.750 --> 01:23:27.750
Malena…

1215
01:23:30.291 --> 01:23:32.000
What I did wasn't planned.

1216
01:23:33.000 --> 01:23:34.291
It just happened.

1217
01:23:36.541 --> 01:23:38.208
I got caught up in it.

1218
01:23:38.291 --> 01:23:41.541
All I wanted was to feel
like someone desired me again.

1219
01:23:43.916 --> 01:23:45.875
Yes. I know it was selfish.

1220
01:23:49.708 --> 01:23:51.375
But you only live once.

1221
01:23:52.041 --> 01:23:54.333
I didn't want to miss my one opportunity.

1222
01:23:55.125 --> 01:23:57.833
-You've never had a fantasy?
-Of course. yes.

1223
01:23:57.916 --> 01:23:59.750
But they stayed fantasies.

1224
01:24:01.000 --> 01:24:03.666
Well. I guess I'm not as in control.

1225
01:24:05.000 --> 01:24:06.500
I suppose not.

1226
01:24:06.583 --> 01:24:07.583
[Lucero sniffles]

1227
01:24:08.625 --> 01:24:10.208
Look. all that I'm asking…

1228
01:24:11.833 --> 01:24:14.541
Is that our children
don't pay for our mistakes anymore.

1229
01:24:16.250 --> 01:24:17.916
Interesting use of "our."

1230
01:24:19.333 --> 01:24:21.166
Please. share custody.

1231
01:24:22.958 --> 01:24:24.875
You have the houses already.

1232
01:24:25.541 --> 01:24:27.666
Don't take their dad from them.

1233
01:24:28.250 --> 01:24:29.583
[sobs]

1234
01:24:31.250 --> 01:24:32.625
[sniffles]

1235
01:24:35.416 --> 01:24:37.166
[policeman] Yes. they're here.

1236
01:24:43.416 --> 01:24:45.000
Okay. there's your dad.

1237
01:24:47.625 --> 01:24:48.875
Careful.

1238
01:24:52.041 --> 01:24:54.041
[indistinct chatter]

1239
01:25:04.500 --> 01:25:06.000
[Lucía] Poor Viviana.

1240
01:25:12.208 --> 01:25:14.833
[vehicle approaches]

1241
01:25:15.333 --> 01:25:18.000
[Lucía] It's going to be okay.
We're here for you.

1242
01:25:18.541 --> 01:25:20.333
[car door opens]

1243
01:25:33.958 --> 01:25:35.750
-You would have done the same as me.
-No.

1244
01:25:37.666 --> 01:25:39.000
I would've never had this issue.

1245
01:25:39.083 --> 01:25:40.916
[chuckles] No?

1246
01:25:41.875 --> 01:25:43.500
Sure thing. Lucero.

1247
01:25:45.458 --> 01:25:46.708
[Lucero] Honey.

1248
01:25:49.000 --> 01:25:52.125
I'm glad you're here.
Everyone's waiting for you.

1249
01:25:54.666 --> 01:25:55.833
Oh.

1250
01:26:00.958 --> 01:26:02.041
Hey.

1251
01:26:04.750 --> 01:26:06.916
-Lucero. Hi.
-Hey.

1252
01:26:07.000 --> 01:26:08.625
[woman 1] How are you?

1253
01:26:12.916 --> 01:26:14.083
Hi.

1254
01:26:16.250 --> 01:26:17.375
How are you?

1255
01:26:18.291 --> 01:26:19.291
[exhales]

1256
01:26:19.375 --> 01:26:20.375
[sniffles]

1257
01:26:21.375 --> 01:26:23.125
-Hello.
-[woman 2] I'm sorry.

1258
01:26:24.541 --> 01:26:27.333
[uneasy music playing]

1259
01:26:27.416 --> 01:26:28.875
I need to get by.

1260
01:26:53.708 --> 01:26:54.916
[sighs]

1261
01:26:55.000 --> 01:26:56.000
[music fades]

1262
01:26:57.125 --> 01:27:00.958
[Julián] Dad said we should stay home.
Why are we doing this?

1263
01:27:03.166 --> 01:27:04.375
[Lucero] Trust me.

1264
01:27:05.250 --> 01:27:07.250
[suspenseful music playing]

1265
01:27:08.708 --> 01:27:11.416
Everything will be fine. I promise.

1266
01:27:12.750 --> 01:27:14.541
How can you be so sure?

1267
01:27:16.333 --> 01:27:17.583
I'll be back.

1268
01:27:19.375 --> 01:27:22.541
-[car door closes]
-[Viviana] Mom. Mom. he's really hurt.

1269
01:27:24.708 --> 01:27:26.000
What do we do?

1270
01:27:28.333 --> 01:27:29.500
[Lucero] It's okay.

1271
01:27:30.125 --> 01:27:31.541
Go with your brother.

1272
01:27:46.791 --> 01:27:48.791
[footsteps approach]

1273
01:28:18.208 --> 01:28:19.250
I knew you'd come.

1274
01:28:21.375 --> 01:28:22.750
I was waiting for you.

1275
01:28:22.833 --> 01:28:24.958
Oh. Matías.

1276
01:28:25.041 --> 01:28:26.916
[Matías] I want us to start over.

1277
01:28:27.000 --> 01:28:28.208
Okay?

1278
01:28:28.291 --> 01:28:33.458
And forget about. uh.
everything that's happened so far. and…

1279
01:28:33.541 --> 01:28:34.791
We can…

1280
01:28:36.041 --> 01:28:39.250
Like that time when you…
When you drove me in your car.

1281
01:28:40.958 --> 01:28:42.250
I…

1282
01:28:42.333 --> 01:28:43.916
I love you so much.

1283
01:28:44.000 --> 01:28:46.500
So. so. so. so much.

1284
01:28:47.000 --> 01:28:48.750
I mean it. really. Lucero. I…

1285
01:28:50.541 --> 01:28:52.916
If you mean it. you will let me go.

1286
01:28:53.000 --> 01:28:54.458
No. no.

1287
01:28:54.541 --> 01:28:56.708
That is impossible. Lucero.

1288
01:28:56.791 --> 01:28:58.666
I can't move on that easily.

1289
01:28:58.750 --> 01:29:00.041
It's impossible.

1290
01:29:00.916 --> 01:29:03.583
I know that. at first.
it will be hard. and…

1291
01:29:03.666 --> 01:29:08.416
It will be difficult. You have to leave
your family and leave your job. and…

1292
01:29:08.500 --> 01:29:10.583
I'm sure it won't be easy. but…

1293
01:29:11.166 --> 01:29:13.125
[breathing heavily] But you'll…

1294
01:29:15.166 --> 01:29:17.583
I know that in time you'll agree.
You'll see it.

1295
01:29:18.500 --> 01:29:20.250
You'll have to trust me.

1296
01:29:21.958 --> 01:29:24.750
Don't make me hurt you. please. Please.

1297
01:29:26.708 --> 01:29:28.625
Don't make me hurt your family.

1298
01:29:30.750 --> 01:29:33.291
[Matías breathing heavily]

1299
01:29:35.000 --> 01:29:37.000
[tense music playing]

1300
01:29:48.291 --> 01:29:49.833
What are you doing?

1301
01:30:06.541 --> 01:30:09.166
[tense music intensifies]

1302
01:30:28.583 --> 01:30:29.916
[grunts]

1303
01:31:04.541 --> 01:31:06.458
[Matías panting]

1304
01:31:08.083 --> 01:31:09.125
[grunts]

1305
01:31:14.125 --> 01:31:16.208
[tense music continues]

1306
01:31:33.416 --> 01:31:35.166
[music fades]

1307
01:31:36.625 --> 01:31:39.625
[breathing shakily]

1308
01:31:43.000 --> 01:31:44.250
[door opens]

1309
01:31:46.083 --> 01:31:47.208
[door closes]

1310
01:31:47.291 --> 01:31:49.541
[suspenseful music playing]

1311
01:32:00.000 --> 01:32:03.041
[car doors open and close]

1312
01:32:10.083 --> 01:32:12.083
[crying]

1313
01:32:17.208 --> 01:32:19.041
Come on. let's go.

1314
01:32:27.375 --> 01:32:29.041
[reporter] A shocking discovery today.

1315
01:32:29.125 --> 01:32:32.083
A young Spanish man
was found dead at the Lomas Club.

1316
01:32:32.166 --> 01:32:34.041
which belongs to Fernando Cortina.

1317
01:32:34.125 --> 01:32:37.500
Lupita Salazar is at the scene
and brings us this report.

1318
01:32:37.583 --> 01:32:38.500
[Salazar] That's right.

1319
01:32:38.583 --> 01:32:42.750
The district attorney of Mexico City was
at the scene and this is what he told us.

1320
01:32:42.833 --> 01:32:46.583
[Miguel] Yes. yes. unfortunately.
one of the swimming instructors.

1321
01:32:46.666 --> 01:32:50.166
who had recently joined the Lomas Club.
was found dead.

1322
01:32:50.250 --> 01:32:53.875
What we know so far is that this young man
was of Spanish nationality.

1323
01:32:53.958 --> 01:32:56.625
and was a professional swimmer
in his country.

1324
01:32:56.708 --> 01:33:00.416
However. a serious addiction
cost him his career.

1325
01:33:00.500 --> 01:33:02.625
We found no signs of external violence.

1326
01:33:02.708 --> 01:33:07.416
and everything seems to indicate that
he took his own life due to his addiction.

1327
01:33:07.500 --> 01:33:09.875
We will give you more details
as they come in.

1328
01:33:09.958 --> 01:33:12.916
The owners of the Lomas Club
are actively cooperating.

1329
01:33:13.000 --> 01:33:16.625
and we hope to be able to return the body
to his country of origin soon.

1330
01:33:16.708 --> 01:33:18.291
Thank you. guys. very much. Excuse me.

1331
01:33:18.375 --> 01:33:21.875
[Salazar] District Attorney Miguel Peña.
Stay tuned for further updates.

1332
01:33:21.958 --> 01:33:23.916
[tense music intensifies]

1333
01:33:24.000 --> 01:33:25.375
[Fernando moans]

1334
01:33:25.458 --> 01:33:27.958
[suspenseful music playing]

1335
01:33:30.000 --> 01:33:32.333
[music fades]

1336
01:33:32.416 --> 01:33:35.000
[sultry music playing]

1337
01:33:40.000 --> 01:33:42.000
[Lucero moans]

1338
01:33:43.000 --> 01:33:45.000
[Fernando grunts]

1339
01:33:57.000 --> 01:33:59.000
[moaning]

1340
01:34:06.250 --> 01:34:08.250
[breathing heavily]

1341
01:34:16.958 --> 01:34:18.958
[sultry music playing]

1342
01:34:52.958 --> 01:34:54.958
[music turns suspenseful]

1343
01:36:05.458 --> 01:36:07.458
[music fades]
